ler%20sitting%20atop%20a%20FA24F%20turbocharged%20horizontally%20opposed%20four-cylinder%20engine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662fd15a0dfb1341e9005fdd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222265%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Subaru%20Ascent's%20FA24F%20turbocharged%20four-cylinder%20engine.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F24F%20debuted%20in%202019%20with%20the%20Ascent%20but%20can%20now%20be%20found%20on%20other%20Subaru%20models%20like%20the%20Outback.%20Here%2C%20it%20produces%20a%20strong%20260%20horsepower%20and%20277%20ft.%20lbs.%20of%20torque.%20It's%20mated%20to%20Subaru's%20Lineartronic%20continuously%20variable%20transmission%20or%20CVT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20Ascent%2C%20equipped%20with%20the%20optional%2020-inch%20wheels%2C%20boasts%20EPA%20fuel%20economy%20figures%20of%2019%20mpg%20city%2C%2025%20mpg%20highway%2C%20and%2021%20mpg%20combined.%20Those%20equipped%20with%2018-inch%20wheels%20are%20about%201%20mpg%20higher%20across%20the%20board.%20The%20EPA%20number%20put%20the%20Ascent%20on%20par%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20Honda%20Pilot%20and%20Hyundai%20Palisades%20but%20falls%20a%20few%20MPG%20short%20of%20the%20Toyota%20Highlander.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20practice%2C%20Subaru's%20EPA%20figures%20are%20pretty%20optimistic.%20On%20our%20test%20car%2C%20we%20hovered%20around%2019%20mpg%20combined%20of%20regular%20unleaded%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20my%202022%20Ascent%2C%20It%20has%20never%20been%20able%20to%20reach%2025%20mpg%20on%20the%20highway.%20In%20fact%2C%20I've%20only%20reached%2023mpg%20once%20in%20highway%20driving.%20Around%20town%2C%20my%20Ascent%20is%20usually%20around%2018mpg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20with%20almost%20all%20Subarus%2C%20the%20Ascent%20is%20equipped%20with%20the%20brand's%20signature%20Symmetrical%20All-Wheel-Drive%20system.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Subaru%20and%20Symmetrical%20all-wheel-drive%20insignias%20are%20emblazoned%20on%20the%20lower%20left%20corner%20of%20the%20Ascent's%20rear%20hatch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662be9f80dfb1341e9ffc81f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESubaru's%20signature%20Symmetrical%20All-Wheel-Drive%20System.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%20Unlike%20many%20AWD%20systems%20found%20in%20competitors%2C%20which%20only%20send%20power%20to%20the%20rear%20wheels%20when%20it%20detects%20traction%20loss%2C%20Subaru's%20system%20constantly%20sends%20power%20to%20all%20four%20wheels.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESo%2C%20what's%20it%20like%20to%20drive%3F%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223556%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20steering%20wheel%20of%20a%20Subaru%20Ascent%20is%20seen%20from%20the%20driver's%20seat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663532a010dfcda40966abf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202024%20Subaru%20Ascent%20Touring%20from%20the%20driver's%20seat.%20%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Subaru%20Ascent%20delivers%20a%20pleasant%20and%20reassuring%20driving%20experience.%20The%20Ascent%20stands%20out%20for%20its%20confident%20handling%20and%20strong%20acceleration%20in%20a%20segment%20that%20doesn't%20prioritize%20driving%20pleasure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20debuted%20in%202019%2C%20I%2C%20along%20with%20many%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20was%20unsure%20about%20pairing%20a%20small%20turbocharged%20four-cylinder%20in%20a%204%2C600-pound%2C%208-passenger%20SUV.%20However%2C%20the%20Subie%20quickly%20proved%20myself%20and%20other%20doubters%20incorrect.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20trendsetter%20as%20others%2C%20like%20the%20Toyota%20Highlander%20and%20Chevrolet%20Traverse%2C%20have%20dumped%20their%20big%20V6%20engines%20in%20favor%20of%20turbo%20fours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Subie%20remains%20peppy%20around%20town%20while%20providing%20gutsy%20acceleration%20down%20the%20highway%20on-ramps.%20The%20Ascent%20never%20felt%20short%20on%20power%2C%20even%20when%20loaded%20with%20cargo%20and%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caranddriver.com%2Freviews%2Fa46009664%2F2023-subaru-ascent-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECar%20and%20Driver%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Ascent%20can%20make%20the%20sprint%20from%20zero%20to%2060mph%20in%20a%20more%20than%20respectable%206.8%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Ascent%20does%20have%20its%20imperfections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20continuously%20variable%20transmission%20is%20the%20weakest%20point%20in%20Ascent's%20driving%20experience%20and%20its%20drive%20train.%20The%20CVTs%20on%20earlier%20Ascents%20including%20my%20own%2C%20can%20feel%20abrupt%20or%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20surge%20when%20accelerating%20at%20lower%20speeds.%20That%20was%20still%20the%20case%20on%20our%202024%20test%20car%20but%20the%20effects%20are%20far%20more%20muted%20and%20barely%20noticeable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20CVT%20whine.%20Upon%20initial%20startup%2C%20the%20Ascent's%20transmission%20emits%20a%20high-pitched%20whining%20noise%20while%20under%20acceleration.%20The%20noise%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20dying%20torque%20converter%20on%20a%20traditional%20automatic%2C%20disappears%20once%20the%20vehicle%20reaches%20normal%20operating%20temperature.%20Even%20though%20the%20transmission%20delivers%20power%20normally%20when%20emitting%20the%20disconcerting%20noise%2C%20it%20feels%20grossly%20out%20of%20place%20in%20a%20%2450%2C000%20SUV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20said%2C%20Subaru's%20Lineartronic%20unit%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20capable%20CVTs%20on%20the%20market%20and%20is%20able%20to%20provide%20a%20serviceable%20approximation%20of%20a%20traditional%20automatic%20transmission.%20The%20pre-programmed%20shift%20points%20that%20mimic%20the%20feel%20of%20an%208-speed%20automatic%20did%20help%20mitigate%20the%20dreaded%20CVT%20drone%20under%20hard%20acceleration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESubaru's%20signature%20EyeSight%20Driver%20Assist%20System%20also%20received%20major%20changes%20in%202023%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20a%20new%20wide-angle%20camera.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ascent%20is%20equipped%20with%20Subaru's%20updated%20EyeSight%20Driver%20Assist%20System%20with%20a%20third%20camera%20mounted%20in%20front%20of%20the%20rear%20view%20mirror.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662bca6023b29110d3038821%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ascent%20now%20features%20Subaru's%20updated%203-camera%20EyeSight%20Driver%20Assist%20System.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESubaru's%20EyeSight%20suite%20of%20driver's%20assistance%20features%20includes%20adaptive%20cruise%20control%20with%20lane%20centering%2C%20lane%20departure%20warning%2C%20pre-collision%20braking%2C%20automatic%20emergency%20steering%2C%20and%20pre-collision%20throttle%20management%2C%20which%20reduces%20power%20from%20the%20engine%20when%20it%20detects%20potential%20danger%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20updated%20system%20to%20be%20excellent%2C%20building%20upon%20the%20strong%20performance%20of%20previous%20iterations.%20I%20found%20the%20system%20less%20intrusive%20and%20smoother%20in%20operation%20than%20the%20unit%20on%20my%202022%20Ascent%20Touring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20adaptive%20cruise%20control%20function%20now%20allows%20for%201%20mile-per-hour%20speed%20adjustments.%20On%202019-2022%20Ascents%2C%20you%20could%20only%20adjust%20the%20speed%20setting%20in%205-mile-per-hour%20increments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20have%20a%20small%20gripe%20with%20the%20adaptive%20cruise%20control%20function.%20The%20steering%20wheel%20buttons%20that%20adjust%20following%20distance%20just%20don't%20make%20sense.%20To%20my%20brain%2C%20the%20button%20with%20an%20arrow%20that%20points%20forward%20toward%20the%20vehicle%20ahead%20should%20reduce%20following%20while%20the%20one%20with%20the%20arrow%20pointing%20backward%20should%20increase%20following%20distance.%20On%20the%20Subaru%2C%20those%20buttons%20do%20the%20exact%20opposite.%20I've%20owned%20my%20Ascent%20for%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20now%20and%20I%20still%20get%20it%20wrong%20when%20I%20use%20adaptive%20cruise%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESubaru's%20new%20DriverFocus%20system%20uses%20a%20camera%20mounted%20on%20top%20of%20the%20front%20dash%20where%20the%20small%20information%20screen%20once%20lived%20to%20scan%20the%20driver's%20eye%20and%20head%20movements%20constantly.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%202024%20Subaru%20Ascent's%20front%20dash%20features%20an%2011.6-inch%20infotainment%20screen%20and%20is%20trimmed%20in%20black%20leather.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6635342a10dfcda40966ae44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22987%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESubaru%20updated%20the%20Ascent's%20dash%20with%20a%20larger%2011.6-inch%20screen.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20the%20feature%20is%20good%20and%20pure.%20It%20gives%20visual%20and%20auditory%20alerts%20to%20the%20driver%20in%20case%20they%20are%20distracted%20or%20fall%20asleep.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20road%20to%20hell%20is%20paved%20with%20good%20intentions%2C%20and%20the%20system%20in%20everyday%20use%20feels%20more%20akin%20to%20an%20overeager%20drill%20sergeant%2C%20ready%20a%20moment's%20notice%20to%20yell%20at%20you%20for%20shifting%20your%20gaze%20to%20adjust%20the%20volume%20knob%20or%20to%20take%20a%20sip%20of%20coffee.%20The%20system%20can%20be%20turned%20off%2C%20but%20will%20automatically%20re-engage%20the%20next%20time%20you%20start%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAscent%20owners%20can%20remotely%20start%2C%20lock%2C%20and%20unlock%20their%20vehicles%20using%20their%20smartphones%20through%20the%20MySubaru%20App.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Subaru's%20MySubaru%20App%20that%20allows%20drivers%20to%20remotely%20start%2C%20lock%2C%20and%20unlock%20their%20vehicles.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6632a29aec0c696569ffe920%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222338%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20MySubaru%20App.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20also%20provides%20diagnostic%20information%20on%20the%20vehicle's%20various%20systems%20and%20allows%20owners%20to%20track%20the%20vehicle's%20location.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESubaru's%20latest%20updates%20keep%20the%20Ascent%20a%20worthy%20option%20for%20those%20seeking%20something%20outside%20the%20status%20quo.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%202024%20Subaru%20Ascent%20Touring%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Publix%20supermarket.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662bb0f60dfb1341e9ff90c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20Subaru%20Ascent%20test%20car%20in%20its%20natural%20environment%2C%20the%20supermarket%20parking%20lot.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20reviewed%20the%20Subaru%20Ascent%20back%20in%202018%2C%20I%20was%20wowed%20by%20its%20user-friendly%20design%2C%20refined%20cabin%2C%20a%20suite%20of%20standard%20safety%20systems%2C%20easy-to-use%20infotainment%2C%20and%20gutsy%20turbocharged%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20that%20remains%20t