mers%20with%20hidden%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FeDreams%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40eDreams%3C%2Fa%3E%20Prime%20Scams%20Exposed!%20%F0%9F%9A%AB%F0%9F%8F%B4%E2%80%8D%E2%98%A0%EF%B8%8F%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAs%20pirate%20OTA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FeDreams%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40eDreams%3C%2Fa%3E%20continues%20to%20promote%20their%20%E2%80%98eDreams%20Prime%20Membership%E2%80%99%2C%20Michael%20takes%20a%20look%20at%20even%20more%20examples%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FeDreams%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40eDreams%3C%2Fa%3E%20overcharging.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERead%20more%20%F0%9F%91%89%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fxhtb4i9JFW%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fxhtb4i9JFW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fscam%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23scam%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FOTApirate%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23OTApirate%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWhichUK%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40whichUK%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fantitrust_it%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40antitrust_it%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCNMC_ES%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40CNMC_ES%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjkIEDeKGKM%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FjkIEDeKGKM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ryanair%20(%40Ryanair)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRyanair%2Fstatus%2F1786006021304926669%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20night%20before%20my%20flight%2C%20I%20measured%20my%20backpack%20and%20found%20it%20was%2010cm%20(4%26quot%3B)%20wider%20than%20Ryanair's%20limit.%20I%20paid%20an%20extra%20%C2%A324%20(%2430)%20for%20a%20larger%20carry-on%20when%20I%20checked%20in%20%E2%80%94%20otherwise%20I%20risked%20a%20%C2%A370%20(%2487)%20fine.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rucksack%20with%20a%20tape%20measure%20laid%20on%20top%20of%20it%20measuring%2035cm%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6632441510dfcda409653928%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222827%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERyanair's%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20bag%26quot%3B%20option%20measures%2040cm%20x%2025cm%20x%2020cm%20(15.7%26quot%3B%20x%209.8%26quot%3B%20x%207.9%26quot%3B).%20You'll%20have%20to%20upgrade%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20risk%20a%20surcharge%20just%20for%20a%20carry-on%20the%20same%20size%20as%20pretty%20much%20any%20other%20airline%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20choose%20this%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20buying%20your%20ticket%2C%20it's%20only%20an%20extra%20%C2%A314%20(%2417)%2C%20so%20I%20lost%20money%20by%20not%20measuring%20my%20bag%20sooner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20I%20could've%20brought%20my%20small%20backpack%20for%20free%20with%20Spirit%2C%20Frontier%2C%20Southwest%2C%20Allegiant%2C%20easyJet%2C%20and%20Wizz%20Air%20%E2%80%94%20to%20name%20just%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECoupled%20with%20choosing%20my%20own%20seat%2C%20this%20meant%20my%20%C2%A335%20ticket%20was%20now%20%C2%A367%20(%2483)%2C%20practically%20doubling%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20ticket.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222478%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20from%20the%20Ryanair%20website's%20booking%20process%20shows%20how%20a%2010kg%20bag%20costs%20%C2%A327.50%20and%20a%2020kg%20bag%20costs%20%C2%A332.49.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662294b820b15f0ff429a306%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221178%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERyanair%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERyanair's%20checked%20luggage%20prices%20change%20depending%20on%20the%20route%20as%20well%20as%20the%20season.%20Two%20carry-on%20bags%20cost%20between%20%C2%A36%20and%20%C2%A338%20(%247.50%20to%20%2447.50)%2C%20while%20one%2020kg%20bag%20costs%20between%20%C2%A318.99%20and%20%C2%A359.99%20(%2424%20to%20%2475).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20particularly%20silly%20fee%20is%20the%20option%20to%20have%20your%20flight%20details%20sent%20via%20SMS%20for%20%C2%A32.99%20(%243.75)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERyanair's%20main%20UK%20hub%20is%20at%20London%20Stansted%20Airport%2C%20which%20isn't%20really%20in%20London%20at%20all.%20As%20the%20crow%20flies%2C%20it's%2031%20miles%20away%20from%20the%20center.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Passengers%20walking%20through%20Stansted%20Airport%20on%20April%2015%2C%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66310e9cec0c696569ff1ea3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20most%20%26quot%3BLondon%26quot%3B%20airports%20are%20outside%20the%20city.%20But%20Stansted%20is%20the%20second%20farthest%20from%20the%20middle%2C%20only%20behind%20Southend%2C%20which%20is%20much%20less%20popular.%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F6Ns5n%2F3%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Most%20London%20airports%20aren't%20in%20London%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22528%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EStansted%20Airport%20saw%2028%20million%20passengers%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%2014%20times%20as%20many%20as%20Southend%20Airport%2C%20which%20is%20about%205%20miles%20farther%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20it%20saves%20the%20airline%20money%2C%20Ryanair%20is%20somewhat%20notorious%20for%20flying%20to%20airports%20far%20away%20from%20where%20you%20actually%20want%20to%20be.%20Among%20the%20most%20egregious%20examples%20are%20Paris-Beauvais%20Airport%2C%2055%20miles%20from%20the%20city%20center%2C%20and%20Germany's%20Frankfurt%20Hahn%20Airport%2C%20which%20is%20almost%2080%20miles%20from%20Frankfurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20woke%20up%20at%205%20a.m.%20in%20order%20to%20make%20it%20to%20Stansted%20for%20my%208%3A40%20a.m.%20flight%20to%20Madrid.%20Then%20I%20took%20the%20Tube%20to%20Tottenham%20to%20catch%20the%20Stansted%20Express%2C%20which%20cost%20%C2%A323.50%20(%2430)%20with%20a%20young%20person's%20discount.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sign%20reads%20%26quot%3BTottenham%20Hale%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20directions%20to%20Stansted%20Airport%20at%20the%20London%20Underground%20station.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6631079c0dfb1341e900adb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20train%20to%20Luton%20Airport%20is%20%C2%A316.90%20(%2421.10)%2C%20while%20taking%20the%20Tube%20to%20Heathrow%20Airport%20is%20%C2%A35.60%20(%247).%20So%20getting%20to%20Ryanair's%20hub%20airport%20again%20increases%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFrom%20its%20starting%20point%20at%20central%20London's%20Liverpool%20Street%20Station%2C%20the%20train%20takes%2048%20minutes%20to%20reach%20the%20airport.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20comfier%20than%20the%20usual%20commuter%20train.%20It%20also%20has%20level%20boarding%20and%20plenty%20of%20luggage%20space.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20down%20the%20aisle%20of%20the%20Stansted%20Express%20train.%20Luggage%20racks%20are%20visible%20on%20the%20side%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20seats%20with%20black%20leather%20headrests%20and%20a%20moquette%20pattern%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663107f6ec0c696569ff181b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222460%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20finally%20arrived%20at%20Stansted%20and%20luckily%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20drop%20any%20bags%20or%20check%20in.%20Remember%20to%20check%20in%20on%20the%20Ryanair%20app%20at%20least%202%20hours%20before%20the%20departure%20time%2C%20or%20you'll%20be%20charged%20%C2%A355%20(%2468)%20at%20the%20airport.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222851%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yellow%20signs%20with%20the%20Ryanair%20logo%20as%20people%20line%20up%20for%20the%20check%20in%20desk%20and%20bag%20drop%20at%20Stansted%20Airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663108a210dfcda40964d5e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222138%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20fee%20was%20%C2%A310%20when%20it%20was%20first%20introduced%20but%20has%20since%20risen.%20It's%20a%20frequent%20cause%20for%20complaints%2C%20with%20the%20BBC%20reporting%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-66500479%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelderly%20couple%20being%20%26quot%3Bhorrified%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20extra%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20allowed%20to%20check%20in%20at%20the%20airport%20for%20free%20if%20you%20add%20the%20%26quot%3BPlus%26quot%3B%20bundle%20that%20comes%20with%20a%2020kg%20checked%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20found%20a%20bag%20sizer%20here%2C%20and%20was%20surprised%20when%20I%20managed%20to%20fit%20my%20backpack%20inside.%20But%20I'm%20still%20pleased%20I%20played%20it%20safe%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20end%20up%20in%20the%20scenario%20of%20getting%20a%20fine.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20rucksack%20in%20a%20Ryanair%20bag%20sizer%20at%20the%20airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66310a20ec0c696569ff19ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20bag%20wasn't%20fully%20packed%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20it%20could%20still%20fit%20in%20the%20parameters.%20As%20Business%20Insider%20paid%20for%20the%20flight%2C%20I%20was%20more%20motivated%20to%20pay%20extra%20to%20ensure%20there%20was%20no%20fine%2C%20which%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20easy%20to%20explain%20to%20my%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20had%20priority%20boarding%20because%20it%20came%20with%20booking%20the%20larger%20carry-on%20option.%20Nobody%20seemed%20to%20care%20how%20big%20the%20bags%20were.%20Several%20people%20seemed%20to%20have%20backpacks%20much%20larger%20than%20mine%20as%20well%20as%20their%20carry-on%20suitcase.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bored%20passengers%20stand%20in%20a%20small%20corridor%20at%20Stansted%20Airport%20waiting%20to%20board%20a%20Ryanair%20plane.%20In%20the%20foreground%20a%20man%20has%20a%20very%20large%20backpack.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66324a0910dfcda409653d86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20priority%20option%20includes%20one%20larger%20carry-on%20and%20one%20personal%20item%2C%20so%20clearly%20there%20was%20leeway%20with%20the%20latter%2C%20even%20on%20a%20busy%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20roommate%20flew%20with%20Ryanair%20not%20long%20after%20me%2C%20and%20opted%20to%20risk%20it%20with%20a%20backpack%20slightly%20larger%20than%20the%20airline's%20limits.%20He%20was%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20being%20held%20in%20a%20small%20corridor%20for%20a%20while%2C%20we%20were%20released%20onto%20the%20tarmac%20and%20ambled%20over%20to%20the%20Boeing%20737-800.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Passengers%20boarding%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800%20at%20Stansted%20Airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66310aa6ec0c696569ff1a1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20jet%20on%20Flightradar24%2C%20boarding%20opened%20almost%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20landed%20%E2%80%94%20highlighting%20Ryanair's%20quick%20turnaround%20time%20which%20lets%20its%20planes%20fly%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBoeing%20has%20specifically%20built%20stairs%20that%20fold%20out%20of%20Ryanair's%20planes%20so%20there's%20no%20need%20for%20airport%20operations%20to%20bring%20a%20jet%20bridge%20or%20stairs%2C%20again%20saving%20time.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223696%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20the%20stairs%20on%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800%20with%20the%20carrier's%20logo%20visible%20on%20a%20step%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66310b3710dfcda40964d85a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222772%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-passenger-compensated-33-000-after-breaking-leg-on-staircase-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EA%20passenger%20on%20budget%20airline%20Ryanair%20was%20awarded%20over%20%2430%2C000%20in%20damages%20after%20she%20fell%20on%20'narrow%20and%20steep'%20plane%20steps%20and%20broke%20her%20leg%20in%202%20places%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20the%20biggest%20surprise%20came%20when%20I%20boarded%20and%20found%20my%20seat%2C%2016D%2C%20was%20in%20an%20exit%20row.%20I%20had%20paid%20an%20extra%20%C2%A38%20to%20ensure%20I%20was%20in%20the%20aisle%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20this%20review%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20had%20I%20really%20gone%20as%20far%20as%20booking%20extra%20legroom%3F%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20emergency%20exit%20row%2C%20Row%2016%2C%20on%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6631109510dfcda40964de48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20double-checked%20the%20seating%20plans.%20Ryanair's%20website%20lists%20row%2016%20as%20a%20normal%20one%20which%20costs%20less%20than%20an%20exit%20row%20seat.%20The%20map%20for%20the%20newer%20737%20Max%208%20was%20displayed%20instead%20of%20the%20737-800's%20slightly%20different%20one.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221494%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20seat%20map%20on%20a%20Ryanair%20booking%20page%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66311a8710dfcda40964e6a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERyanair%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20I'd%20paid%20%C2%A38%20rather%20than%20%C2%A315%20confused%20me.%20I%20presume%20this%20could%20mean%20somebody%20paying%20for%20extra%20legroom%20in%20row%2018%2C%20but%20ending%20up%20in%20a%20regular%20seat%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ryanair%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20this%20flight%20was%20originally%20scheduled%20to%20operate%20on%20a%20Boeing%20737-Max%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Boeing%20737-Max%20seat%20map%20displayed%20in%20this%20passenger%20booking%20flow%20for%20this%20flight%20to%20Stansted%20to%20Madrid%20(15%20Apr).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20operational%20reasons%2C%20the%20aircraft%20was%20changed%20to%20a%20Boeing%20737-800%20model%2C%20which%20has%20a%20slightly%20different%20seat%20layout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20regular%20seat%20has%2030%26quot%3B%20of%20legroom%20but%20also%20doesn't%20recline.%20I%20thought%20the%20leather%20looked%20pretty%20worn%2C%20although%20the%20jet%20is%2013%20years%20old.%20It%20was%20still%20relatively%20comfy%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20complaints.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223408%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ryanair%20flight%20attendant%20helps%20a%20woman%20put%20her%20bag%20in%20the%20overhead%20bin%20while%20most%20of%20the%20seats%20remain%20empty%20during%20boarding%2C%20as%20viewed%20from%20the%20aisle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66311b4710dfcda40964e725%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221704%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHowever%2C%20one%20thing%20which%20wasn't%20comfortable%20was%20my%20vision%2C%20given%20the%20garish%20yellow-and-navy%20color%20scheme%20along%20with%20adverts%20on%20the%20overhead%20bins.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cabin%20of%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800%20in%20its%20yellow%20and%20blue%20color%20scheme%20with%20commercials%20on%20the%20overhead%20bins%2C%20as%20viewed%20from%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20aisle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66310c2310dfcda40964d9ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnother%20unique%20design%20point%20of%20a%20Ryanair%20jet%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20seat%20pocket%2C%20with%20the%20safety%20card%20printed%20on%20the%20headrest%20instead.%20Again%2C%20this%20is%20to%20save%20time%20between%20flights%20as%20there's%20less%20to%20clean.%20Although%20I%20prefer%20the%20pocket%20as%20it's%20handy%20for%20storing%20a%20book%20or%20a%20water%20bottle.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223312%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20back%20of%20a%20seat%20on%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800%20is%20mostly%20navy%20but%20yellow%20at%20the%20headrest%2C%20with%20the%20safety%20card%20printed%20onto%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66311140ec0c696569ff21ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222484%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20exit%20row%2C%20it%20took%20me%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20fidgeting%20to%20find%20my%20tray%20table%2C%20which%20folded%20out%20of%20the%20armrest.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20folded%20in%20half%2C%20where%20there's%20a%20dint%20for%20a%20drink%20holder.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tray%20table%20on%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800%20exit%20row%20seat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663115a90dfb1341e900bc7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20we%20took%20off%2C%20I%20went%20to%20explore%20the%20bathroom.%20It%20was%20a%20pretty%20good%20size%20and%20I%20thought%20there%20was%20plenty%20of%20room%20for%20my%205'9'%20frame.%20Ryanair%20had%20its%20own%20no-smoking%20notice%20written%20in%20eight%20different%20languages.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Business%20Insider's%20Pete%20Syme%20takes%20a%20selfie%20in%20the%20mirror%20of%20a%20bathroom%20onboard%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66325d8410dfcda409655564%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStories%20of%20Ryanair%20passengers%20having%20too%20much%20to%20drink%20or%20smoking%20in%20the%20bathroom%20aren't%20uncommon%20in%20the%20British%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-passenger-caught-smoking-in-toilet-hauled-off-flight-police-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVideo%20shows%20police%20hauling%20a%20Ryanair%20passenger%20off%20a%20flight%20after%20he%20was%20caught%20smoking%20in%20the%20plane's%20toilet%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20also%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20bathroom%20had%20company%20branded%20bottles%20of%20soap%2C%20which%20felt%20almost%20too%20luxurious%20for%20Ryanair.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bottle%20of%20Ryanair-branded%20soap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663117f910dfcda40964e46f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShortly%20after%20the%20trolley%20service%20began%2C%20the%20seatbelt%20sign%20came%20on%20for%20turbulence.%20The%20trolley%20was%20only%20a%20row%20away%20from%20me%2C%20but%20never%20returned%20even%20when%20the%20seatbelt%20sign%20went%20off%20again.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Ryanair%20flight%20attendants%20push%20a%20trolley%20down%20the%20aisle%2C%20with%20pringles%20and%20scratch%20cards%20and%20cigarettes%20on%20top%2C%20from%20the%20aisle%20seat's%20point%20of%20view.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6632587b10dfcda409654dcd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221494%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20plan%20on%20spending%20even%20more%20money%20by%20buying%20food%20or%20drink%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20mention%20scratch%20cards%20or%20duty-free%20cigarettes%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20I%20was%20never%20even%20given%20the%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20wasn't%20that%20impressed%20by%20the%20flight%20attendants%20overall.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ryanair%20flight%20attendant%20passes%20magazine%20to%20a%20customer%20sitting%20on%20board%20a%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663240650dfb1341e901144e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ryanair%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20greetings%20when%20we%20boarded%20and%20the%20whole%20affair%20was%20quite%20unsmiling.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it's%20a%20strictly%20no-frills%20airline%2C%20and%20they%20work%20long%20shifts%20so%20I'm%20not%20disgruntled%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20noting%20the%20cabin%20crew%20on%20similar%20airlines%20like%20easyJet%20and%20Wizz%20Air%20are%20definitely%20friendlier%20in%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20enjoyed%20the%20flight%20and%20there%20weren't%20really%20any%20problems%2C%20although%20tannoy%20announcements%20hawking%20duty-free%20products%20were%20a%20bit%20annoying.%20With%20no%20in-flight%20entertainment%20or%20airline%20magazine%2C%20I%20was%20happy%20to%20read%20a%20novel.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20page%20of%20the%20novel%20%26quot%3BMoney%26quot%3B%20by%20Martin%20Amis%20is%20displayed%20on%20a%20Ryanair%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663256aeec0c696569ff921a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%