-johnathan-buma-chs-genius-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeter%20Thiel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20to%20those%20who%20know%20him%20from%20his%20days%20in%20London%20and%20Zurich%2C%20California%20Forever%20represents%20a%20strange%20and%20unlikely%20new%20chapter%20in%20Sramek's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshort%20and%20not%20entirely%20successful%20career.%20The%20question%20is%20not%20just%20does%20Sramek%2C%20working%20with%20an%20impressive%20team%20of%20urban%20planners%2C%20have%20the%20answer%20to%20what%20ails%20America's%20cities.%20The%20question%20is%20also%3A%20Does%20he%20really%20have%20a%20shot%20at%20building%20it%2C%20where%20all%20others%20have%20failed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20England%2C%20back%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20Jan%20Sramek%20was%20a%20name%20to%20conjure%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20born%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20small%20town%20called%20D%C5%99evohostice.%20His%20mother%20was%20a%20teacher%2C%20his%20father%20a%20mechanic.%20His%20grandparents%20worked%20in%20the%20local%20steel%20mill.%20In%202004%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017%2C%20Sramek%20bailed%20on%20all%20that.%20He%20enrolled%20in%20boarding%20school%20in%20the%20city%20of%20York%2C%20in%20England%2C%20and%20two%20years%20later%20took%2010%20A-level%20exams%2C%20the%20British%20university%20entrance%20tests.%20Sramek%20got%20A's%20on%20all%2010.%20Nobody%20takes%20that%20many%20A-levels%2C%20let%20alone%20scores%20A's%20on%20every%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA-level%20exams%20are%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20Britain's%20socioeconomic%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%94%20ace%20them%2C%20and%20they're%20like%20the%20chain%20that%20pulls%20a%20roller%20coaster%20uphill%2C%20a%20mechanism%20for%20upward%20mobility.%20When%20a%20working-class%20kid%20from%20Eastern%20Europe%20did%20it%2C%20the%20feat%20earned%20a%20mention%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Feducation%2F2006%2Faug%2F17%2Fschools.alevels3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enational%20press%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20years%20Sramek%20was%20a%20role%20model%20for%20other%20English%20kids%20with%20aspirations.%20His%20name%20would%20pop%20up%20on%20forums%20where%20students%20discussed%20strategies%20for%20getting%20into%20their%20dream%20universities.%20Only%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestudentroom.co.uk%2Fshowthread.php%3Ft%3D1972204%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20weeks%20to%20ace%20an%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20%26quot%3BJan%20Sramek%20says%20it%20can%20be%20done.%20You%20have%20to%20focus%20and%20be%20disciplined.%26quot%3B%20If%20Jan%20could%20do%20it%2C%20maybe%20you%20could%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20A-levels%20got%20Sramek%20into%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20left%20after%20just%20a%20year%2C%20for%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20square%20mile%20of%20London%20that's%20Europe's%20answer%20to%20Wall%20Street.%20%26quot%3BParty%20boy%20Jan%20is%20youngest%20Rising%20Star%20in%20Square%20Mile%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.standard.co.uk%2Fhp%2Ffront%2Fparty-boy-jan-is-youngest-rising-star-in-square-mile-6758772.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etabloid%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20in%20school%2C%20he%20kept%20busy%20launching%20his%20own%20business%20ventures.%20There%20was%20AlphaParties%2C%20which%20he%20touted%20as%20the%20go-to%20organizer%20for%20parties%20at%20some%20of%20London's%20glitziest%20establishments%2C%20though%20Sramek%20claimed%20that%20he%20himself%20never%20drank%20or%20smoked.%20There%20was%20a%20careers%20website%20called%20Nicube.%20But%20his%20main%20focus%20was%20the%20internship%20he%20landed%20in%20London%20with%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20081026082242%2Fhttps%3A%2Fdavidlanger.co.uk%2F2008%2F10%2F23%2Ftycoons-of-tomorrow-1-jan-sramek%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%202008%20blog%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20series%20titled%20%26quot%3BTycoons%20of%20Tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20Sramek%20said%20he%20slept%20only%20five%20hours%20a%20night.%20His%20role%20model%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20Thiel%2C%20the%20PayPal%20cofounder%20and%20early%20investor%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-peter-thiel-svb-facebook-trump-biography-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Asked%20what%20motivated%20him%2C%20Sramek%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3Bracing%20against%20myself.%26quot%3B%20His%20advice%20for%20other%20budding%20entrepreneurs%3A%20%26quot%3BSee%20everything%20in%20terms%20of%20risk-reward%2C%20almost%20like%20a%20trade.%20Determine%20your%20entry%2C%20exit%20and%20stop%20loss.%20Know%20when%20to%20get%20out.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20Goldman%20interns%20hoped%20to%20convert%20the%20entry-level%20position%20into%20a%20full-time%20gig.%20Sramek%20actually%20pulled%20it%20off.%20In%202009%2C%20he%20became%20a%20trader%20on%20the%20firm's%20emerging-markets%20desk.%20In%20his%20spare%20time%2C%20he%20cowrote%20%26quot%3BRacing%20Towards%20Excellence%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bro-ish%20self-help%20book.%20The%20next%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20150822202225%2Fhttps%3A%2Fwww.cheatsheet.com%2Ffeatures%2Fexclusive-wall-st-cheat-sheet-top-3-traders-under-30.html%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECheatSheet%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Sramek%20was%20being%20mentored%20by%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20of%20London's%20most%20powerful%20hedge%20fund%20managers%20who%20are%20clearly%20grooming%20him%20for%20the%20very%20top.%26quot%3B%20New%20York%20magazine%20ascribed%20to%20Sramek%20a%20%26quot%3Bcocksure%20arrogance.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-the-22-year-old-goldman-employee-who-is-the-youngest-ever-on-the-rising-starsfn100-2009-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThis%20very%20publication%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bprodigy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20it%20was%20a%20little%20early%20for%20all%20that.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20cart%20before%20the%20horse%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20a%20friend%20of%20Sramek's%20from%20Cambridge%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20around%20this%20guy%2C%20but%20he%20hadn't%20really%20delivered%20much%20in%20the%20real%20world.%26quot%3B%20Jonas%20Rave%2C%20a%20colleague%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20says%20Sramek%20was%20charismatic%20and%20confident.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20curse%20of%20the%20gifted%20child%20who's%20told%20from%20an%20early%20age%20that%20they're%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20Rave%20says.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20early%20success%20that%20makes%20you%20believe%20you%20can%20do%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESramek%20left%20Goldman%20after%20a%20bit%20less%20than%20two%20years%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tenure%20so%20short%20that%20internet%20trolls%20and%20a%20few%20fellow%20bankers%20cocked%20their%20eyebrows%20at%20what%20might%20have%20gone%20wrong%20for%20the%20wunderkind.%20His%20managers%2C%20though%2C%20back%20up%20Sramek's%20account%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20leave%20was%20his.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20very%20gifted%2C%20high-potential%20employee%2C%20but%20he%20had%20very%20ambitious%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Guy%20Saidenberg%2C%20a%20former%20Goldman%20partner%20who%20oversaw%20Sramek's%20division.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20was%20a%20bit%20frustrated%20at%20the%20speed%20he%20was%20being%20promoted%20and%20given%20responsibilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESramek%20moved%20to%20Zurich%2C%20where%20he%20followed%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20many%20former%20traders%3A%20He%20tried%20to%20launch%20a%20hedge%20fund.%20At%20first%20he%20planned%20to%20use%20a%20technology-guided%20%26quot%3BMoneyball%26quot%3B%20mentality%20to%20improve%20traders'%20batting%20averages.%20But%20after%20testing%20the%20software%20with%20actual%20users%2C%20Sramek%20and%20his%20cofounder%20pivoted.%20Now%20it%20was%20an%20education%20startup.%20They%20changed%20the%20name%20from%20Erudify%20(as%20in%2C%20perhaps%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20make%20more%20erudite%26quot%3B)%20to%20just%20Better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetter%20did%20not%20live%20up%20to%20its%20name.%20Sramek's%20next%20venture%2C%20a%20kind%20of%20supercharged%20version%20of%20Evernote%20called%20Memo%2C%20got%20him%20noticed%20by%20Silicon%20Valley.%20The%20investor%20Marc%20Andreessen%20described%20Memo%20as%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20ideas%20have%20sex.%26quot%3B%20But%20it%20failed%20to%20procreate%2C%20and%20Sramek%20found%20himself%20out%20of%20ideas.%20So%20at%2030%2C%20after%20five%20years%20of%20working%20on%20failed%20startups%2C%20he%20did%20what%20Europeans%20often%20do%20when%20they%20can't%20find%20a%20way%20to%20succeed%20on%20the%20continent.%20He%20set%20out%20to%20reinvent%20himself%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shadow%20across%20Jan%20Sramek's%20face%20in%20front%20of%20a%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a9a380dfb1341e9ff3ff4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJan%20Sramek%20stands%20for%20a%20portrait%20on%20an%20old%20farm%20in%20Solano%20County.%20The%20property%20was%20the%20second%20piece%20of%20land%20that%20Sramek%20purchased%20in%20the%20area...%3Cp%3EChristie%20Hemm%20Klok%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ESramek%20had%20spent%20years%20reading%20about%20the%20Bay%20Area's%20success%20as%20a%20hub%20of%20jobs%20and%20innovation.%20But%20when%20he%20finally%20moved%20there%20in%202015%2C%20he%20found%20longtime%20residents%20protesting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprotesters-block-google-buses-with-piles-of-scooters-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20buses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-pain-worsens-workers-visitors-shoppers-leave-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20attracting%20the%20smartest%20people%20in%20the%20world%2C%20paying%20them%20egregious%20amounts%20of%20money%2C%20and%20building%20precisely%20no%20places%20for%20them%20to%20live.%20So%20they%20were%20fighting%20over%20the%20existing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenrys-leaving-west-coast-sunbelt-california-texas-florida-real-estate-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehousing%3C%2Fa%3E%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20outsider%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20see%20how%20we%20messed%20up%20the%20housing%20market%20here%20in%20a%20really%20profound%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Sramek%20says.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20everyone%20getting%20excited%20about%20good-paying%20jobs%2C%20it%20was%3A%20Yeah%2C%20good-paying%20jobs%2C%20but%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20displaced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20pleasant%20parts%20of%20Bay%20Area%20cities%2C%20the%20kinds%20of%20places%20young%20people%20and%20young%20families%20might%20want%20to%20go%2C%20were%20prohibitively%20expensive.%20%26quot%3BMy%20girlfriend%20and%20I%20were%20making%20good%20money%2C%20and%20we%20struggled%20to%20live%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-generative-ai-san-francisco-hayes-silicon-cerebral-valley-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHayes%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Sramek%20says%2C%20name-checking%20what's%20arguably%20the%20cutest%20neighborhood%20in%20America's%20cutest%20city.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20tournament%20with%20a%20fixed%20number%20of%20slots.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20Sramek%20started%20reading%20%E2%80%94%20in%20two%20years%2C%20he%20claims%2C%20he%20devoured%20500%20books%20about%20urban%20development.%20(You%20can%20do%20the%20math%20and%20decide%20for%20yourself%20whether%20that%20sounds%20plausible.)%20The%20standout%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20%26quot%3BThe%20Death%20and%20Life%20of%20Great%20American%20Cities.%26quot%3B%20Sramek%2C%20like%20generations%20of%20readers%20before%20him%2C%20was%20taken%20by%20Jane%20Jacobs'%20emphasis%20on%20the%20value%20of%20vibrant%2C%20diverse%20streetfronts%20and%20the%20need%20to%20mix%20residences%20with%20retail.%20He%20traveled%20the%20world%2C%20studying%20the%20most%20popular%20neighborhoods%20in%20the%20most%20vibrant%20cities%2C%20from%20Atlanta%20and%20Phoenix%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdenmark-maternity-hotel-room-service-nurses-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECopenhagen%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Barcelona.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20just%20walk%20them%20for%20two%20days%20and%20see%20what%20worked%2C%26quot%3B%20Sramek%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESramek%20exudes%20a%20specific%20kind%20of%20brainy%20charm.%20He's%20good-looking%20and%20speaks%20English%20with%20a%20slight%20Eastern%20European%20accent%3B%20he%20wears%20brown%20suede%20desert%20boots%20and%20sports%20a%20suitably%20weathered%20black%20Goruck%20GR1%20backpack%2C%20an%20emblem%20of%20techy%2C%20tactical%20coolness.%20He's%20also%20a%20quick%20study.%20Embracing%20the%20ideals%20of%20the%20modern%20city%2C%20he%20decided%20that%20what%20is%20needed%20is%20cheaper%20housing%20(to%20reduce%20inequality)%2C%20solar%20power%20and%20wind%20farms%20(to%20reduce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frichest-americans-income-creates-outsized-emissions-climate-crisis-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbon%3C%2Fa%3E%20emissions)%2C%20and%20more%20densely%20populated%2C%20walkable%20neighborhoods%20(to%20support%20shops%20and%20restaurants%2C%20create%20jobs%2C%20and%20reduce%20commute%20times).%20Yet%20it's%20hard%20to%20build%20places%20like%20that%20nowadays%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20host%20of%20zoning%20and%20land-use%20rules%20designed%20to%20protect%20the%20environment%20and%20promote%20public%20input.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESramek's%20new%20business%20idea%20was%20pretty%20far%20removed%20from%20his%20youthful%20grindcore%20mindset.%20Forget%20software%20startups%3B%20in%20the%20real%20world%20he'd%20do%20real%20estate.%20Sramek%20thought%20he'd%20build%20in%20the%20interstitial%20and%20vacant%20spaces%20in%20cities.%20Planners%20call%20that%20%3Cem%3Einfill%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20fashionable%20idea%20in%20urbanism%20%E2%80%94%20supplying%20the%20%26quot%3Bmissing%20middle%26quot%3B%20between%20single-family%20homes%20and%20bulky%20apartment%20buildings.%20There%20was%20only%20one%20problem.%20Bay%20Area%20cities%20have%20created%20a%20process%20for%20permitting%20new%20buildings%20so%20byzantine%2C%20slow%2C%20and%20expensive%20that%20if%20the%20great%20New%20York%20builder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistorian-robert-caro-on-interviewing-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobert%20Moses%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20alive%20and%20trying%20to%20work%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20he'd%20be%20more%20Power%20Broken%20than%20Power%20Broker.%20Sramek's%20idea%20got%20nowhere.%20So%20to%20take%20his%20mind%20off%20his%20troubles%2C%20he%20went%20fishing%20%E2%80%94%20literally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20avid%20angler%2C%20Sramek%20had%20been%20spending%20time%20on%20the%20waters%20of%20the%20Sacramento-San%20Joaquin%20River%20Delta%2C%20the%20northwestern%20corner%20of%20San%20Francisco%20Bay.%20To%20get%20there%2C%20he%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20would%20drive%20through%20Solano%20County%2C%20dotted%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20old%20farms%2C%20strip%20malls%2C%20half-empty%20downtowns%2C%20and%20industry%20in%20various%20states%20of%20disarray.%20On%20one%20fishing%20trip%2C%20Sramek%20noticed%20an%20empty%20diamond-shaped%20space%20between%20Travis%20Air%20Force%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-plans-to-keep-c5-cargo-planes-flying-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBase%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20town%20of%20Rio%20Vista.%20To%20make%20his%20point%2C%20he%20calls%20up%20a%20satellite%20view%20of%20the%20land%20on%20his%20Tesla's%20screen%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20a%20bit%20disconcerting%2C%20given%20that%20he's%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20that%20it's%20the%20only%20yellow%20patch%20on%20the%20map%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20On%20the%20satview%2C%20everything%20around%20the%20empty%20diamond%20is%20the%20beige-gray%20of%20city%20or%20the%20lush%2C%20irrigated%20green%20of%20maintained%20land.%20It%20seems%20like%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%20%E2%80%94%20until%20Sramek%20zooms%20out.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20%3Cem%3Eeverywhere%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%20triumphantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20yellow%20diamond%20is%20between%20San%20Francisco%20and%20Sacramento.%20Between%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20the%20ski-and-sun%20resorts%20of%20Lake%20Tahoe.%20It's%20the%20geographic%20center%20of%20the%20Bay%20Area%20megaregion.%20And%20it's%20almost%20as%20big%20as%20Toledo%2C%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20key%20that%20unlocked%20the%20problem%20Sramek%20had%20been%20struggling%20with.%20The%20way%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esolve%20the%20housing%20crisis%20that's%20killing%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20he%20decided%2C%20wasn't%20with%20small-bore%20infill.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20never%20going%20to%20be%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20if%20you%20could%20build%20walkable%20neighborhoods%20on%20a%20greenfield%20site%3F%26quot%3B%20Why%20fix%20an%20old%20city%20like%20San%20Francisco%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20when%20you%20could%20build%20a%20brand-new%20one%20an%20hour%20north%20in%20Solano%20County%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20leans%20against%20the%20Model%20Y%2C%20looking%20out%20at%20the%20wide%2C%20flat%20space%20his%20company%20owns%2C%20Sramek's%20eyes%20unfocus%20a%20little.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20good%20place%20for%20a%20subdivision%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20connected%20to%20an%20existing%20town.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20jobs.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20entertainment%20or%20retail.%26quot%3B%20It%20becomes%20something%20only%20if%20you%20bring%20in%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20homes%2C%20jobs%2C%20shops%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20houses%20of%20worship.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20want%20to%20build%20it%20at%20that%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jan%20Sramek%20looking%20over%20a%20map%20on%20top%20of%20his%20car.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a9b0f0dfb1341e9ff4041%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpen%20on%20the%20hood%20of%20Jan%20Sramek's%20new%20Rivian%20are%20the%20original%20maps%20of%20Solano%20County.%20The%20maps%20show%20the%20current%20growth%20of%20the%20area%20and%20the%20predicted%20future%20growth.y%3Cp%3EChristie%20Hemm%20Klok%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESramek%20named%20his%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-billionaires-flannery-associates-solano-county-mystery-utopian-city-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Flannery%20Road%2C%20a%20gravel%20road%20running%20across%20the%20site%2C%20and%20convened%20a%20top-notch%20team%20of%20urban%20planners%20to%20assist%20him.%20%26quot%3BJan%20has%20a%20pretty%20extraordinary%20vision%20for%20seeing%20this%20opportunity%20and%20putting%20it%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20BH%20Bronson%20Johnson%2C%20the%20project's%20sustainability%20engineer%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20on%20big%20urban%20projects%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-treasure-island-6-billion-dollar-development-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETreasure%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20Google's%20since-canceled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falphabet-sidewalk-labs-abandons-project-for-quayside-toronto-neighborhood-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESidewalk%3C%2Fa%3E%20neighborhood%20in%20Toronto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESramek%20was%20certainly%20thinking%20big.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20provide%20homes%20for%20Bay%20Area%20techies%20and%20jobs%20for%20Solano%20County.%20But%20he%20couldn't%20convince%20anyone%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20project.%20So%20he%20took%20out%20a%20loan%20and%20bought%20the%20first%20bits%20of%20the%20yellow%20part%20of%20the%20map%20himself.%20He%20won't%20say%20how%20much%20the%20loan%20was%20for.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20didn't%20work%2C%20I%20would've%20been%20in%20deep%20trouble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20loan%20also%20paid%20for%20feasibility%20studies%20on%20the%20site.%20The%20engineering%20analysis%20concluded%20that%20it%20was%20the%20ideal%20place%20to%20build%20a%20new%20city%3A%20too%20lousy%20to%20farm%2C%20no%20tectonic%20activity%2C%20high%20enough%20to%20withstand%20even%20the%20direst%20estimates%20of%20sea-level%20rise.%20Armed%20with%20the%20detailed%20studies%2C%20Sramek%20made%20another%20run%20at%20wealthy%20investors.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20wore%20people%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20would%20say%2C%20'This%20is%20a%20good%20idea%2C%20and%20here%20are%20150%20reasons%20it%20won't%20work.'%20And%20I%20would%20take%20them%20one%20by%20one.%20At%20some%20point%2C%20people%20run%20out%20of%20questions.%20And%20then%20they%20invested.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESramek%20impressed%20the%20titans%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20just%20as%20he%20had%20charmed%20his%20way%20into%20the%20upper%20echelons%20of%20high%20finance%20in%20his%20college%20days.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20about%20investing%20in%20the%20people%20behind%20those%20big%20ideas%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20David%20George%2C%20the%20partner%20at%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20handling%20the%20firm's%20investment%20in%20California%20Forever.%20%26quot%3BJan%20is%20a%20man%20on%20a%20mission%2C%20and%20a%20student%20of%20history%2C%20geography%2C%20and%20what%20makes%20cities%20special.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20Big%20Tech%2C%20Sramek%20was%20able%20to%20acquire%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-billionaires-flannery-associates-solano-county-mystery-utopian-city-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eland%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20needed%20for%20California%20Forever.%20Now%20all%20he%20needed%20was%20permission%20to%20build%20something%20on%20it.%20But%20that%2C%20he%20soon%20discovered%2C%20might%20take%20California%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Marilyn%20Farley%20started%20hearing%20rumors.%20Farmers%20in%20Solano%20County%20were%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-california-forever-farmers-pressured-to-sell-land-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epressured%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolano-county-flannery-associates-city-of-yesterday-silicon-valley-billionaires-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esell%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20city%20councilwoman%2C%20Farley%20was%20no%20stranger%20to%20fighting%20out-of-town%20developers.%20Way%20back%20in%201984%2C%20a%20local%20group%20named%20the%20Solano%20County%20Orderly%20Growth%20Committee%20formed%20to%20block%20a%20San%20Francisco%20developer%20who%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20new%20city%2C%20from%20scratch%2C%20on%20mostly%20empty%20land%20near%20Travis%20Air%20Force%20Base.%20To%20keep%20others%20from%20trying%20the%20same%20thing%2C%20the%20committee%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Farley%20would%20join%20a