efused%20to%20sell%2C%20Flannery%20took%20them%20to%20court%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20colluding%20to%20force%20the%20price%20higher.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20landowners%20claimed%20that%20Sramek%20had%20pitted%20family%20members%20against%20each%20other%20as%20a%20tactic%20to%20strong-arm%20farmers%20into%20selling%20their%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Sramek%20had%20been%20hoping%20to%20win%20over%20the%20locals%2C%20he%20was%20off%20to%20a%20bad%20start.%20He%20had%20effectively%20staged%20a%20secret%20land%20grab%20with%20stealth%20funding%20provided%20by%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20wealthiest%20tech%20barons.%20%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20why%20that%20looks%2C%20on%20the%20surface%2C%20odd%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20now%20concedes.%20But%20he%20points%20to%20another%20California%20visionary%20who%20secretly%20bought%20up%20land%20before%20unveiling%20his%20dream%20of%20Tomorrowland.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Disney%20was%20building%20Disney%20World%2C%20that's%20what%20he%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Sramek%20says.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20all%20love%20Disney%20World.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solano%20County%20and%20Rio%20Vista%20residents%20Kathleen%20Threlfall%2C%20left%2C%20and%20Bill%20Mortimore%20protest%20outside%20a%20press%20conference%20with%20a%20sign%20reading%20%26quot%3BNot%20Invited%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a95130dfb1341e9ff3c6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESolano%20County%20and%20Rio%20Vista%20residents%20Kathleen%20Threlfall%2C%20left%2C%20and%20Bill%20Mortimore%20protest%20outside%20a%20press%20conference%20unveiling%20California%20Forever's%20plans%20after%20being%20shut%20out%20of%20the%20event%20held%20in%20Rio%20Vista%2C%20Calif.%2C%20Jan.%2017%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EJessica%20Christian%2FSan%20Francisco%20Chronicle%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EForced%20into%20the%20open%2C%20Sramek%20shifted%20his%20strategy%20to%20one%20of%20transparency.%20He%20released%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-forever-silicon-valley-billionaire-city-plans-are-terrible-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20preliminary%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20began%20personally%20answering%20emails%20from%20concerned%20citizens%2C%20and%20met%20with%20Farley.%20She%20describes%20him%20as%20cordial%2C%20though%20she%20was%20immune%20to%20his%20charisma.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20he%20has%20his%20mind%20made%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20says.%20%26quot%3BHe%20knows%20what%20he%20wants%20to%20do.%20He%20has%20money%2C%20and%20he's%20used%20to%20getting%20his%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20got%20even%20uglier%20last%20November%2C%20when%20Sramek%20attended%20a%20public%20meeting%20about%20the%20project%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eat%20the%20Vallejo%20Naval%20and%20Historical%20Museum.%20The%20audience%20tore%20him%20to%20shreds.%20Why%20did%20Sramek%20buy%20all%20that%20land%20in%20secret%2C%20they%20demanded.%20Why%20should%20they%20trust%20him%3F%20One%20person%20who%20attended%20said%20Sramek%20sounded%20like%20Lyle%20Lanley%2C%20the%20con%20artist%20who%20sells%20the%20town%20of%20Springfield%20a%20monorail%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv4z_9NcIJXI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20classic%20%26quot%3BSimpsons%26quot%3B%20episode%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20others%2C%20Sramek%20came%20across%20as%20unapologetic%20and%20arrogant%2C%20treating%20Solano%20as%20an%20engineering%20challenge%20instead%20of%20a%20real%20place.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20these%20founders%20and%20investors%20speak%20very%20logically%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sam%20Houston%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-of-vallejo-california-what-its-like-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVallejo%3C%2Fa%3E%20resident%20who%20was%20also%20there.%20%26quot%3BIt%20all%20makes%20sense%20to%20them.%20But%20this%20is%20more%20than%20just%20logic.%20This%20is%20where%20people%20live.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20experienced%20members%20of%20Sramek's%20team%20weren't%20surprised%20by%20the%20backlash.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20been%20to%20hundreds%20of%20community%20planning%20meetings%20in%20my%20career%2C%20what%20I%20have%20seen%20in%20Solano%20County%20is%20absolutely%20common%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Gabriel%20Metcalf%2C%20the%20head%20of%20urban%20planning%20for%20California%20Forever.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20go%20and%20take%20your%20lumps.%20You've%20got%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20make%20the%20argument.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESramek%20realizes%20he%20screwed%20up.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20this%20to%20be%20about%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20do%20a%20good%20job%20of%20telling%20the%20story.%26quot%3B%20And%20if%20he%20can't%20undo%20the%20damage%2C%20there%20may%20never%20be%20a%20California%20Forever.%20To%20get%20around%20the%20anti-development%20law%20Farley's%20committee%20helped%20pass%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20Sramek%20is%20pushing%20a%20ballot%20measure%20that%20would%20rezone%20his%20property.%20He%20has%20tried%20to%20appease%20locals%20by%20agreeing%20to%20invest%20in%20Solano's%20battered%20downtowns%2C%20and%20he%20has%20moved%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20young%20children%20to%20the%20area.%20He's%20also%20begun%20playing%20up%20his%20working-class%20roots.%20Whether%20Sramek%20has%20the%20Midas%20touch%20may%2C%20ironically%2C%20come%20down%20to%20whether%20he%20can%20master%20the%20common%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20moves%20have%20failed%20to%20allay%20the%20concerns%20of%20many%20local%20leaders.%20Rep.%20John%20Garamendi%2C%20the%20congressman%20who%20was%20worried%20about%20a%20Chinese%20government%20invasion%2C%20still%20isn't%20on%20board.%20He%20says%20the%20newest%20version%20of%20Sramek's%20plan%20doesn't%20account%20for%20the%20water%20and%20roads%20and%20schools%20that%20California%20Forever's%2050%2C000%20residents%20will%20need.%20Like%20many%20locals%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdemocrats-propose-renaming-miami-prison-after-trump-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGaramendi%3C%2Fa%3E%20continues%20to%20distrust%20the%20larger%20motivations%20of%20Sramek%20and%20his%20Silicon%20Valley%20investors.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20he's%20doing%20is%20a%20scam%2C%26quot%3B%20Garamendi%20says.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20going%20to%20build%20a%20city.%20He's%20taking%2016%2C000%20acres%2C%20maybe%2020%2C000%20acres%2C%20and%20getting%20it%20rezoned.%20Then%20he's%20going%20to%20sell%20that%20land%20to%20somebody%20that%20is%20a%20developer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20California%20Forever%20has%20an%20existential%20problem%2C%20it's%20not%20that%20it's%20too%20ambitious%2C%20or%20that%20its%20investors%20are%20rich%20hypocrites%20who%20would%20never%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsee-inside-investor-marc-andreessens-33-million-house-for-sale-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrade%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%2010%20acres%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-inside-atherton-california-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAtherton%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20row%20house%20in%20Foreverville.%20It's%20that%20the%20project%2C%20despite%20its%20lofty%20claims%2C%20isn't%20really%20a%20city.%20It's%20a%20glorified%20subdivision%20that's%20designed%20to%20look%20and%20function%20like%20a%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20Jane%20Jacobs%2C%20Sramek%20and%20his%20team%20of%20urban%20planners%20have%20created%20an%20idealized%20version%20of%20modern%20urban%20living.%20There%20are%20townhouses%20and%20affordable%20condos%20in%20place%20of%20single-family%20homes%2C%20and%20cozy%20little%20coffee%20shops%20on%20the%20cobblestone%20streets%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcycling-boom-us-streets-infrastructure-bike-lanes-history-united-states-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebike%20paths%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20everywhere.%20There's%20even%20a%20%26quot%3Bwarehouse%20district%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20neighborhood%20full%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20buildings%20that%2C%20in%20an%20organic%20city%2C%20would%20have%20been%20repurposed%20from%20their%20industrial-era%20uses%20into%20artists%20lofts%20and%20caf%C3%A9s%20and%20boutiques.%20Everything%20in%20California%20Forever%20is%20imagineered%2C%20a%20simulacrum%20of%20a%20city.%20And%20because%20it%20doesn't%20have%20a%20job%20base%20to%20speak%20of%2C%20the%20people%20who%20live%20there%20will%20have%20to%20drive%20to%20and%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-industry-fake-work-problem-bad-managers-bosses-layoffs-jobs-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20day%2C%20just%20like%20all%20the%20other%20suburban%20commuters.%20Sure%2C%20they'll%20have%20bike%20paths%20at%20home.%20But%20outside%20of%20Foreverville%2C%20they'll%20still%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20highways%20to%20get%20to%20the%20real%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20here's%20the%20thing%3A%20California%20Forever%20may%20be%20a%20subdivision%2C%20but%20it's%20precisely%20the%20kind%20of%20subdivision%20America%20needs%20right%20now.%20Rather%20than%20slapping%20up%20a%20bunch%20of%20energy-sucking%20McMansions%20or%20soulless%20lots%20dotted%20with%20cookie-cutter%20houses%2C%20Sramek%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20something%20that's%20both%20vibrant%20and%20sustainable.%20He%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20create%20jobs%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20he%20can%20create%20affordable%20housing%20and%20car-free%20streets%20and%20neighborhoods%20that%20are%20friendly%20to%20commerce%20and%20community%20and%20kids.%20Dismiss%20him%2C%20if%20you%20will%2C%20as%20another%20plundering%2C%20technocratic%20developer%20intent%20on%20making%20millions%20for%20himself%20and%20his%20technocratic%20investors.%20But%20at%20least%20his%20blueprint%20for%20plundering%20would%20help%20solve%20the%20housing%20crisis%20and%20reduce%20inequality%20and%20protect%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20folks%20who%20live%20in%20nearby%20towns%20like%20Fairfield%20and%20Vallejo%2C%20Sramek%20points%20out%2C%20aren't%20against%20development%20in%20principle.%20After%20all%2C%20subdivisions%20are%20already%20springing%20up%20on%20the%20edges%20of%20what%20is%20now%20Sramek's%20property.%20One%20of%20those%20projects%2C%20One%20Lake%2C%20is%20a%20seemingly%20typical%20collection%20of%20houses%20a%20mile%20or%20so%20from%20Travis%20Air%20Force%20Base.%20The%20first%20hint%20that%20it's%20different%20is%20the%20blocky%20apartment%20building%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20town%20%E2%80%94%20affordable%20housing%20that%20was%20part%20of%20the%20deal%20to%20get%20One%20Lake%20built.%20The%20larger%20difference%20is%20obvious%20as%20soon%20as%20Sramek%20drives%20his%20Tesla%20past%20the%20%26quot%3BWelcome%20to%20One%20Lake%26quot%3B%20sign.%20There's%20a%20lake%20%E2%80%94%20an%20artificial%20one.%20And%20on%20its%20shore%20is%20a%20gorgeous%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20all%20glass%20and%20exposed%20wood%20beams%2C%20called%20Journey%20Coffee.%20It's%20a%20coffeehouse%2C%20maybe%20bigger%20and%20airier%20than%20one%20you'd%20find%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-austin-buy-a-home-texas-tech-jobs-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAustin%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Cambridge%2C%20but%20with%20a%20similar%20menu%3B%20the%20seasonal%20special%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bminty%20mocha%20latte.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20Lake%20neighborhood%20with%20houses%20being%20built%20in%20front%20of%20a%20man-made%20river.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a9b920dfb1341e9ff4056%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2240