merates%20like%20LVMH%20and%20Diageo%2C%20and%20two%20more%20are%20set%20to%20open.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EScotch%20whisky%20is%20easy%20to%20find%20on%20the%20island%3B%20there%20are%20even%20cases%20lining%20the%20airport%20waiting%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20people%20from%20Islay%2C%20from%20our%20taxi%20driver%20to%20former%20distillery%20workers%2C%20still%20spoke%20about%20a%20cask%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollector-pays-almost-20-million-cask-scotch-whisky-made-1975-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScotch%20whisky%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Ardbeg%20distillery%20that%20was%20bought%20by%20an%20unnamed%20collector%20for%20%2420%20million%20back%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20recently%20there%20to%20visit%20the%20reopening%20of%20Port%20Ellen.%20This%20distillery%20has%20only%20operated%20for%2017%20of%20the%20last%2094%20years%20but%20has%20become%20a%20cult%20favorite%20with%20whisky%20aficionados.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20distillery%20shut%20down%20in%201983%20and%20has%20been%20sitting%20dormant%2C%20housing%20casks%20of%20aging%20whisky%20ever%20since.%20Renewed%20interest%20in%20the%20liquor%20and%20diminishing%20stocks%20led%20parent%20company%20Diageo%20to%20pour%20%C2%A3185%20million%20(%24230%20million)%20into%20reopening%20Port%20Ellen%20and%20another%20distillery%2C%20Brora%2C%20and%20improving%20its%20Scotch%20whiskey%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20visited%20Port%20Ellen%20on%20the%20day%20it%20reopened%20in%20March%20to%20find%20out%20why%20people%20pay%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20for%20its%20single-malt%20Scotch%20whisky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPort%20Ellen%20Distillery%20closed%20in%201983%20due%20to%20a%20slump%20in%20the%20whisky%20market%2C%20which%20left%20them%20with%20more%20supply%20than%20they%20knew%20what%20to%20do%20with.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22exterior%20of%20Port%20Ellen%20Whisky%20distillery%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660be3943f923f7dab036de6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Bacon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20distillery%20was%20established%20in%201825%20and%20operated%20until%201983.%20Since%20then%2C%20it's%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bghost%26quot%3B%20distillery%2C%20which%20refers%20to%20a%20distillery%20that%20has%20closed%20but%20still%20has%20stock%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20shutting%20down%20gave%20the%20whisky%20time%20to%20mature%20into%20its%20signature%20smoky%20taste%2C%20and%20it%20became%20increasingly%20sought%20after%20by%20whisky%20fans.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22entrance%20to%20the%20Port%20Ellen%20Distillery%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660becae16bde8d4ead46e16%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Bacon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20limited%20stock%20means%20that%20it's%20an%20expensive%20product%3B%20prices%20can%20stretch%20up%20to%20%C2%A345%2C000%20(%2456%2C000)%20for%20a%20set%20of%20two%20bottles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENow%20it's%20reopening%20to%20the%20new%20fans%20it's%20gradually%20gained%20over%20the%20last%2040%20years.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plinths%20with%20port%20ellen%20whisky%20on%20top%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660be47d1caec1275a6badb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Bacon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20distillery%20is%20clearly%20made%20to%20appeal%20to%20a%20premium%20customer.%20Diageo%20commissioned%20artist%20%3Cspan%3EHarry%20Morgan%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20design%20plinths%20to%20showcase%20its%20whisky%20in%20the%20warehouse.%20Visitors%20can%20even%20take%20a%20mini%20version%20of%20these%20plinths%20home%20with%20them%20as%20a%20memento%20for%20their%20coffee%20table%20if%20they%20have%20%C2%A33%2C900%20(%244%2C800)%20to%20spare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20one%20of%20the%20plinths%20was%20a%20Port%20Ellen%20whisky%20from%201980%2C%20one%20of%20only%20a%20limited%20number%20bottled%20to%20commemorate%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II's%20visit%20to%20the%20distillery.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20bottle%20of%20port%20ellen%20whisky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660bea3b3f923f7dab036e56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Bacon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDiageo%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20bought%20this%20whisky%20back%20on%20the%20secondary%20market.%20The%20company%20didn't%20comment%20on%20how%20much%20it%20paid%20to%20get%20the%20bottle%20back%2C%20but%20its%20value%20on%20the%20secondary%20market%20was%20lower%20than%20usual%20as%20it%20has%20a%20sip%20taken%20out%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20company%20says%20could%20have%20been%20from%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bottle%20pictured%20is%20actually%20a%20replica%2C%20the%20real%20one%20is%20too%20valuable%20to%20be%20displayed%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVisitors%20to%20the%20distillery%20will%20be%20able%20to%20choose%20from%20two%20tours.%20The%20least%20expensive%20tour%20comes%20in%20at%20%C2%A3200%20(%24250)%20distillery%20and%20the%20price%20of%20the%20more%20premium%20%26quot%3BAtlas%20of%20Smoke%26quot%3B%20experience%20is%20available%20on%20request%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Port%20ellen%20distillery%20lounge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660be9b216bde8d4ead46dd9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20h