n%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVisitors%20on%20the%20Atlas%20of%20Smoke%20tour%20will%20also%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20draw%20directly%20from%20one%20of%20these%20casks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOver%20in%20the%20distillery%2C%20these%20copper%20stills%20are%20used%20to%20produce%20the%20classic%20Port%20Ellen-style%20whisky%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Whisky%20Stills%20in%20Port%20Ellen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660be6401caec1275a6badd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPort%20Ellen%20is%20a%20distillery%20on%20the%20Isle%20of%20Islay%2C%20an%20island%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Scotland.%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Bacon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EPhoenix%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3B%20Stills%20are%20precise%20replicas%20of%20the%20original%20Port%20Ellen%20stills%20and%20are%20used%20to%20recreate%20the%20classic%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20experimental%20stills%20are%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20That's%20where%20private%20clients%20can%20choose%20to%20tailor%20the%20whisky%20to%20their%20own%20tastes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Whisky%20distillation%20process%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660be84d1caec1275a6badf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Bacon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20experimental%20stills%20will%20allow%20distillers%20to%20change%20the%20depth%20and%20smokiness%20of%20the%20liquid%20depending%20on%20private%20clients'%20tastes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESince%20the%20whisky%20will%20take%20years%20to%20mature%2C%20there's%20little%20concern%20that%20the%20reopening%20will%20bring%20down%20prices.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2240