mall%20percentage%20were%20in%20a%20position%20to%20take%20action.%20I%20could%20offer%20comfort%2C%20but%20sometimes%2C%20it%20felt%20a%20bit%20like%20I%20was%20rearranging%20the%20deck%20chairs%20of%20the%20Titanic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%2C%20though%2C%20that%20this%20was%20a%20business%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20was%20good%20at%20it.%20So%2C%20I%20went%20on%20to%20do%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpreferred-college-life-oxford-over-college-us-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPh.D.%20at%20Oxford%20in%20Theology%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20wanted%20to%20understand%20how%20Western%20philosophy%20defined%20intuition.%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20intuition%20as%20it%20pertained%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20%26quot%3Bgifts%20from%20God.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EConsulting%20for%20businesses%20was%20more%20rewarding%20than%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20poverty%20of%20student%20life%20pushed%20me%20to%20make%20money%20doing%20intuitive%20work.%20Many%20clients%20approached%20me%2C%20and%20some%20started%20asking%20me%20to%20look%20at%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%2C%20if%20I%20could%20look%20at%20life%2C%20why%20not%20look%20at%20business%20and%20try%20to%20get%20the%20same%20information%3F%20So%20I%20did%20it%20and%20it%20worked%2C%20and%20I%20made%20an%20awful%20lot%20of%20money%20for%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20was%20so%20profitable%20that%20these%20clients%20started%20recommending%20me%20to%20their%20friends%20in%20other%20businesses%20and%20industries.%20I%20had%20entertainment%20agents%20coming%20to%20me%2C%20including%20people%20at%20big%20television%20networks%2C%20clients%20in%20fashion%2C%20and%20some%20in%20finance.%20I%20oversaw%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions.%20I%20worked%20with%20several%20hedge%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20initially%20reluctant%20to%20consult%20for%20businesses%2C%20the%20move%20helped%20me%20find%20more%20meaning%20in%20my%20work.%20By%20and%20large%2C%20the%20businesses%20I%20worked%20with%20are%20not%20good%20forces%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20capitalist%20extractive%20machines.%20What%20I%20could%20do%2C%20though%2C%20was%20pivot%20the%20mindsets%20of%20the%20individuals%20I%20advised%20to%20bring%20positive%20changes.%20Sometimes%2C%20that%20was%20as%20simple%20as%20adjusting%20the%20culture%20to%20benefit%20those%20who%20needed%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20work%20with%20clients%20if%20we%20have%20synergy.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20I%20spend%20most%20of%20my%20time%20sharing%20my%20work%20for%20free%20on%20social%20media%20and%20working%20behind%20the%20scenes%20on%20projects%20that%20further%20liberation.%20I%20earn%20money%20by%20advising%20wealthy%20people%20like%20Hollywood%20celebrities%2C%20agents%2C%20producers%2C%20etc.%20I'm%20excited%20about%20art%20and%20creativity.%20I%20advise%20on%20scripts%2C%20plot%20lines%2C%20and%20the%20endings%20of%20television%20shows%20and%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20only%20based%20on%20referrals.%20I%20usually%20set%20up%20an%20introductory%20call%20with%20the%20client.%20If%20I'm%20working%20with%20a%20corporation%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20in%20contact%20with%20someone%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-headhunters-executive-search-board-csuite-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboard%20or%20in%20the%20C%20Suite%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20I%20have%20energetic%20access%20to%20the%20decision-making%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20paid%20by%20results%2C%20so%20I%20need%20to%20know%20that%20the%20energy%20I'm%20putting%20in%20will%20be%20profitable%20for%20my%20client%20and%20myself.%20I%20only%20move%20forward%20if%20there's%20synergy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20then%20onwards%2C%20I%20have%20a%20call%20or%20an%20in-person%20meeting%20once%20a%20month.%20All%20of%20my%20client%20relationships%20include%20absolute%20access%20to%20me%20in%20all%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20spiritual%20clients%20pay%20me