ot%3BAnd%20so%20I'm%20just%20going%20in%20and%20saying%2C%20'Hey%2C%20it's%20gonna%20be%20a%20good%20day.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20a%20few%20months%2C%20the%2027-year-old%20risk%20management%20advisor%20has%20found%20himself%20getting%20recognized%20offline.%20While%20meeting%20with%20BI%20in%20Boston%2C%20Clarke%20was%20approached%20by%20several%20people%20walking%20by%2C%20including%20a%20college%20student%2C%20an%20Amazon%20tech%20worker%2C%20and%20a%20middle-aged%20lawyer%2C%20who%20all%20asked%20for%20selfies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20inspiring.%20That's%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryker%20Puls%2C%20the%20Amazon%20employee%20on%20vacation%20from%20Seattle%2C%20said%20of%20Clarke's%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvariably%2C%20Clarke%20will%20ask%20his%20fans%20about%20their%20day%2C%20where%20they%20work%2C%20and%20maybe%20even%20the%20name%20of%20their%20dog.%20After%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20conversation%2C%20he'll%20often%20urge%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bstay%20locked%20in%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bget%20fired%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETom%20Ranucci%2C%20an%20IT%20worker%20and%20food%20blogger%2C%20met%20Clarke%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Massachusetts%20at%20Amherst.%20He%20described%20Clarke%20was%20%26quot%3Bfull%20of%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20someone%20excited%20to%20meet%20anyone%20and%20everyone%20and%20chat%20about%20anything%20and%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20the%20exact%20same%20person%26quot%3B%20in%20real%20life%2C%20Ranucci%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20stayed%20in%20touch%20after%20college%20thanks%20in%20part%20to%20their%20shared%20interest%20in%20running%20(Clarke's%20explosive%20finish%20at%20the%20Boston%20Marathon%20last%20month%20went%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boston.com%2Fnews%2Fboston-marathon%2F2024%2F04%2F17%2Fdavis-clarke-boston-marathon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eviral%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Ranucci%20never%20expected%20his%20friend's%20social%20media%20following%20to%20skyrocket%20the%20way%20it%20did%20earlier%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20though%20he%20wasn't%20surprised%20that%20the%20message%20found%20an%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20mind%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%2C%20Clarke%20never%20expected%20to%20become%20a%20phenomenon.%20Besides%20a%20barely-used%20Facebook%20account%2C%20his%20digital%20footprint%20was%20almost%20nonexistent%20until%20a%20class%20project%20his%20freshman%20year%20of%20college.%20The%20assignment%3F%20Build%20a%20social%20media%20account%20and%20use%20it%20to%20show%20the%20world%20the%20values%20he%20cared%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20set%20out%2C%20I%20truly%20just%20wanted%20to%20get%20people%20confident%20and%20fired%20up%20to%20go%20after%20their%20goals.%20I%20try%20to%20stay%20true%20to%20that%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20isn't%20under%20any%20illusions%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20content.%20Clarke%20knows%20there%20are%20people%20out%20there%20doing%20%26quot%3Bway%20more%26quot%3B%20interesting%20things%20than%20his%20daily%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20just%20showing%20normal%20life%2C%20and%20the%20good%20side%20of%20it%2C%20is%20what%20gets%20people%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20interesting%20because%20so%20many%20people%20out%20there%20are%20working%20hard%2C%20doing%20all%20these%20same%20things%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20positive%20outlook%20doesn't%20mean%20everybody%20loves%20his%20content.%20Some%20doubt%20that%20he%2C%20or%20anyone%2C%20can%20seemingly%20always%20be%20so%20genuinely%20enthusiastic.%20Other%20commenters%20just%20think%20it's%20repetitive%20or%20annoying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Clarke%20says%20he's%20not%20worried%20about%20the%20hate%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20he's%20glad%20that%20it's%20getting%20more%20people%20to%20engage%20with%20his%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20gives%20me%20a%20chance%20to%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20try%20to%20take%20someone%20who's%20negative%20and%20make%20them%20pause.%20Let's%20show%20them%20what%20we're%20doing%2C%20show%20them%20why%20we're%20doing%20what%20we're%20doing.'%20Just%20try%20to%20earn%20their%20respect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20thinks%20some%20of%20the%20comments%20are%20good-natured%20trash%20talk%2C%20rather%20than%20people%20being%20%26quot%3Bgenuinely%20mean.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20say%20the%20comments%20are%20like%20a%20community%20of%20their%20own%2C%20so%20maybe%20that's%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20be%20creative%2C%20they'll%20come%20up%20with%20funny%20things%20like%20they'll%20be%20like%20'bad%20day%20to%20be%20a%20spreadsheet%2C'%20'bad%20day%20to%20be%20a%20whatever.'%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20ever%20came%20up%20with%20that%20at%20all.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERanucci%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bcertainly%26quot%3B%20thinks%20that%20Clarke's%20content%20gets%20people%20to%20approach%20their%20boring%2C%20everyday%20routine%20differently%2C%20%26quot%3Bjust%20because%20how%20infectious%20his%20energy%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20contagious%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20laugh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20see%20that%20and%2C%20you%20know%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20not%20to%20join%20right%20in%2C%20and%20take%20that%20same%20love%20and%20passion%20into%20what%20they're%20doing%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20own%20lives%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavis-clarke-positive-tiktok-videos-locked-in-office-culture-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714900921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6634f2e9ec0