2ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Talks%20With%20China%20Going%20Well%3A%20Rajnath%20Singh%20On%20Ladakh%20Border%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20military%20standoff%20between%20India%20and%20China%20drags%20on%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20the%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20are%20going%20on%20well%20and%20indicated%20hope%20for%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20lingering%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20PTI%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20also%20said%20that%20India%20has%20been%20developing%20infrastructure%20along%20the%20frontier%20with%20China%20at%20a%20rapid%20speed%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20country's%20borders%20will%20remain%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20talks%20are%20going%20on%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20declining%20to%20elaborate%20further%20considering%20the%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20the%20dialogue%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20he%20was%20hopeful%20of%20a%20positive%20outcome%20and%20an%20end%20to%20the%20nearly%20four-year%20face-off%20between%20the%20two%20militaries%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20shot%20back%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20no%20hope%2C%20then%20why%20to%20have%20talks.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20Chinese%20side)%20also%20have%20hope%20and%20that%20is%20why%20holding%20the%20talks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20militaries%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20standoff%20since%20May%202020%20and%20a%20full%20resolution%20of%20the%20border%20row%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20achieved%20though%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20disengaged%20from%20a%20number%20of%20friction%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20minister%20also%20took%20a%20potshot%20at%20the%20Congress%20for%20continuously%20targeting%20the%20government%20on%20the%20eastern%20Ladakh%20standoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(Congress)%20are%20questioning%20the%20bravery%20of%20Indian%20soldiers%20...%20who%20are%20you%20demoralising%3F%20What%20is%20your%20intention%3F%20I%20can%20also%20go%20back%20to%201962%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20nosedived%20significantly%20following%20the%20fierce%20clash%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020%20that%20marked%20the%20most%20serious%20military%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20maintaining%20that%20its%20ties%20with%20China%20cannot%20be%20normal%20unless%20there%20is%20peace%20in%20the%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20held%20the%20last%20round%20of%20high-level%20military%20talks%20in%20February%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20resolve%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20was%20no%20indication%20of%20a%20breakthrough%20at%20the%2021st%20round%20of%20talks%2C%20both%20sides%20agreed%20to%20maintain%20%26quot%3Bpeace%20and%20tranquillity%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20continue%20the%20communication%20on%20the%20way%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20round%20of%20military%20talks%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Army%20Chief%20Gen%20Manoj%20Pande%20said%20the%20situation%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20is%20%26quot%3Bstable%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%26quot%3B%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20Indian%20troops%20are%20maintaining%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20high%20state%26quot%3B%20of%20operational%20preparedness%20to%20effectively%20deal%20with%20any%20eventualities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGen%20Pande%20also%20said%20that%20both%20India%20and%20China%20continue%20to%20hold%20talks%20at%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20levels%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20return%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bstatus%20quo%20ante%26quot%3B%20that%20existed%20in%20the%20middle%20of%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eastern%20Ladakh%20border%20standoff%20erupted%20on%20May%205%2C%202020%2C%20following%20a%20violent%20clash%20in%20the%20Pangong%20lake%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20a%20series%20of%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20talks%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20completed%20the%20disengagement%20process%20in%20several%20friction%20points%2C%20including%20on%20the%20north%20and%20south%20banks%20of%20the%20Pangong%20lake%20and%20in%20the%20Gogra%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714899900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F0pljj3a_rajnath-singh-_625x300_22_April_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftalks-with-china-going-well-rajnath-singh-on-ladakh-border-row-5593172%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20military%20standoff%20between%20India%20and%20China%20drags%20on%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20the%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20are%20going%20on%20well%20and%20indicated%20hope%20for%20a%20resolution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftalks-with-china-going-well-rajnath-singh-on-ladakh-border-row-5593172%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftalks-with-china-going-well-rajnath-singh-on-ladakh-border-row-5593172%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftalks-with-china-going-well-rajnath-singh-on-ladakh-border-row-5593172%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Eurovision%20entrant%20addresses%20'extreme'%20remarks%20on%20Israel's%20inclusion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714899900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com