2%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Floud-cheers-as-virat-kohli-makes-lively-gesture-towards-anushka-sharma-watch%2Farticleshow%2F109856276.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opposition%20Has%20Not%20Taken%20Up%20Issues%20Consistently%3A%20RLD's%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20chief%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20delved%20into%20a%20myriad%20of%20electoral%20intricacies%2C%20offering%20insights%20into%20the%20unfolding%20political%20landscape%20as%20India%20braces%20itself%20for%20crucial%20phases%20of%20voting.%20From%20the%20impact%20of%20diminished%20voter%20turnout%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20the%20looming%20electoral%20battlegrounds%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary's%20perspectives%20painted%20a%20picture%20of%20both%20anticipation%20and%20apprehension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20his%20concerns%20over%20the%20dwindling%20voter%20participation%2C%20particularly%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20emphasized%20the%20need%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20to%20explore%20innovative%20strategies%20to%20engage%20younger%20and%20urban%20voters.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20about%20casting%20votes%3B%20it's%20about%20fostering%20an%20environment%20where%20every%20citizen%20feels%20compelled%20to%20exercise%20their%20democratic%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20remarked.%20Despite%20the%20lackluster%20turnout%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20noted%20the%20unwavering%20commitment%20of%20certain%20voter%20segments%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20electoral%20contest%20in%20western%20UP%20was%20far%20from%20being%20a%20close%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20the%20challenge%20for%20both%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20and%20opposition%20in%20mobilizing%20their%20respective%20voter%20bases%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary