e%20audience's%20overwhelming%20support.%20Reflecting%20on%20their%20journey%2C%20Sunny%20remarked%20on%20the%20family's%20longstanding%20presence%20in%20the%20industry%20since%20the%201960s.%20Despite%20their%20popularity%2C%20they%20struggled%20to%20understand%20why%20success%20eluded%20them%20until%20recent%20years.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20release%20of%20'Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani'%2C%20'Gadar%202'%2C%20and%20'Animal'%2C%20they%20were%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20audience's%20love%20and%20support.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsunny-deol-many-labelled-gadar-2-as-old-cinema-from-an-old-director%2Farticleshow%2F109854544.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wrestler%20Bajrang%20Punia%20Suspended%20By%20National%20Anti%20Doping%20Body%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Anti-Doping%20Agency%20(NADA)%20suspended%20wrestler%20Bajrang%20Punia%20indefinitely%2C%20a%20move%20that%20could%20potentially%20jeopardise%20his%20bid%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20later%20this%20year.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20Punia%20failed%20to%20provide%20his%20urine%20sample%20for%20the%20selection%20trials%20at%20Sonepat%20on%20March%2010%2C%20prompting%20NADA%20to%20issue%20the%20order%20suspending%20him%20from%20participation%20in%20any%20future%20events.%20%26quot%3BWith%20subject%20to%20paragraph%204%3A1%3A2%20below%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20article%207.4%20of%20the%20NADR%202021%2C%20Bajrang%20Punia%20has%20been%20immediately%20provisionally%20suspended%20from%20participation%20in%20any%20competition%20or%20activity%20prior%20to%20the%20final%20decision%20reached%20at%20a%20hearing%20in%20this%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20an%20official%20release%20from%20NADA%20dated%20April%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunia%2C%20along%20with%20a%20line%20of%20other%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20Olympians%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Vinesh%3B%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20former%20BJP%20MP%20and%20president%20of%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20suspension%20in%20light%20of%20the%20charges%2C%20Punia%2C%20who%20won%20the%20country%20a%20bronze%20medal%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20barred%20from%20participation%20in%20the%20selection%20trials%20that%20are%20scheduled%20for%20later%20this%20month.%20No%20Indian%20has%20yet%20won%20an%20Olympic%20quota%20in%20the%2065kg%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESujeet%20Kalkal%20will%20represent%20India%20at%20the%20World%20Qualifiers%2C%20which%20are%20set%20to%20get%20underway%20in%20Istanbul%20on%20May%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20notice%20was%20addressed%20to%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India's%20(WFI)%20now-defunct%20ad%20hoc%20committee%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20federation%20that%20is%20recognised%20by%20United%20World%20Wrestling%20(UWW).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunia%2C%20who%20a%20few%20months%20prior%20released%20a%20video%20claiming%20to%20have%20expired%20dope-collecting%20kits%2C%20disregarded%20the%20dope%20control%20officer's%20directive%2C%20claiming%20that%20NADA%20officials%20had%20not%20yet%20addressed%20his%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20dope-collecting%20officer's%20report%2C%20he%20left%20even%20though%20he%20was%20informed%20that%20his%20refusal%20would%20result%20in%20a%20warning%20for%20breaking%20anti-doping%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPunia%2C%20surrounded%20by%20his%20supporters%2C%20continuously%20repeated%20his%20statement%20and%20immediately%20left%20the%20venue%20refusing%20to%20give%20a%20dope%20sample%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DCO%20stated%20in%20his%20r