%20that%20Gabba%20Test%20match.%20Getting%20somebody%20like%20Steve%20Smith%20out%20when%20he%20was%20on%2055...%20so%20this%20is%20the%20real%20strength%20of%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20the%20self-belief%20and%20the%20never-say-die%20attitude%20on%20the%20field.%26quot%3B%20Chasing%20a%20modest%20148%2C%20Faf%20du%20Plessis%20(64)%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20(42)%20put%20on%2092%20runs%20inside%20the%20powerplay%20to%20give%20RCB%20a%20blistering%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCB%2C%20however%2C%20slipped%20from%2092%2F0%20to%20117%2F6%20before%20romping%20home%20in%2013.4%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExtraordinary%20stuff%20during%20the%20power%20play%20when%20RCB%20was%20batting.%20It%20was%20just%20game%20on%2C%20and%20then%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20things%20changed.%20Were%20they%20trying%20to%20counter%20the%20net%20run%20rate%20solution%3F%20And%20if%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20then%20well%20played%20to%20them%20because%20they%20needed%20to%20go%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Australian%20batter%20Matthew%20Hayden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20they%20lost%20those%20three%20wickets%20to%20Joshua%20Little%20straight%20away%20in%20that%20middle%20stage%20of%20the%20match.%20And%20then%20they%20were%20able%20to%20consolidate%20because%2C%20simply%20as%20you%20heard%20Faf%20at%20the%20presentation%20say%2C%20anything%20short%20of%20180%2C%20even%20190%20on%20this%20high-scoring%20venue%2C%20was%20never%20going%20to%20be%20enough%20runs.%26quot%3B%20Former%20England%20cricketer%20and%20coach%20Paul%20Collingwood%20also%20lauded%20the%20%26quot%3Baggressive%20approach%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20RCB%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20intensity%20displayed%20by%20RCB%20with%20the%20ball%20was%20commendable.%20Even%20while%20chasing%20a%20modest%20total%2C%20seeing%20Virat%20Kohli%20stepping%20out%20of%20his%20crease%20and%20effortlessly%20flicking%20a%20delivery%20for%20six%20on%20just%20the%20second%20ball%20indicated%20their%20aggressive%20intent.%20This%20signals%20danger%20for%20their%20opponents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20their%20position%20near%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20table%2C%20RCB%20didn't%20hold%20back.%20They%20showed%20clarity%2C%20bravery%2C%20and%20aggression%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20middle%20order.%20Although%20they%20lost%20wickets%2C%20I%20commend%20their%20aggressive%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714891740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnepmpbpg_sunil-gavaskar-bcci_625x300_05_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fafter-doubling-down-on-virat-kohli-sunil-gavaskar-wins-hearts-with-remarks-on-mohammed-siraj-5592453%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20cricket%20legend%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20had%20earlier%20slammed%20Virat%20Kohli%20for%20hitting%20back%20at%20pundits%20over%20criticism%20of%20his%20strike-rate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Riteish%20Genelia's%20funny%20video%20delights%20Juhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714891665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109854244%2Cimgsize-31652.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Friteish-deshmukh-and-genelia-deshmukhs-funny-video-delights-juhi-chawla%2Farticleshow%2F109854244.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109854244.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBollywood's%20beloved%20couple%2C%20Riteish%20Deshmukh%20and%20Genelia%20Deshmukh%2C%20keep%20fans%20enter