standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmcap-of-6-of-top-10-firms-declines-by-rs-68-417-cr-airtel-biggest-laggard-124050500145_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmcap-of-6-of-top-10-firms-declines-by-rs-68-417-cr-airtel-biggest-laggard-124050500145_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Problem%20With%20Wrongly%20Labelling%20Real%20Or%20Edited%20Videos%20As%20'Deepfakes'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20edited%20video%20of%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20went%20viral%20recently%2C%20falsely%20showing%20him%20promising%20an%20end%20to%20reservations%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes.%20While%20BOOM's%20fact-check%20found%20that%20the%20video%20was%20doctored%20using%20video%20editing%20tools%2C%20it%20was%20falsely%20labelled%20as%20a%20'deepfake'%20by%20other%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%2C%20and%20various%20mainstream%20media%20outlets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%20in%20India%20are%20experimenting%20with%20AI%20in%20myriad%20ways%20this%20election%20season.%20For%20instance%2C%20AI%20voice%20clones%20of%20politicians%20are%20being%20used%20to%20craft%20cadre%20and%20voter%20outreach%20messages.%20Political%20parties%20are%20also%20skirting%20any%20social%20media%20rules%20by%20using%20satirical%20videos%20which%20use%20voice%20cloning%2C%20face%20swap%20and%20other%20AI%20editing%20techniques%2C%20to%20target%20their%20political%20rivals.%20These%20videos%20are%20posted%20on%20their%20official%20Instagram%20and%20YouTube%20handles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20damaging%20deepfakes%20that%20are%20outright%20deceptive%2C%20are%20being%20shared%20either%20by%20IT%20cell%20workers%2C%20or%20through%20proxies%20and%20diffused%20actors%2C%20who%20support%20the%20party%20and%20their%20ideology.%20With%20misinformation%20peaking%20during%20election%20seasons%20in%20India%2C%20shallow%20fakes%20or%20cheapfakes%20still%20make%20up%20most%20of%20the%20misinformation%20seen%20online%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fgbe5ul48_deepfake_625x300_05_May_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ENot%20Always%20Deepfakes%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20mainstream%20media%20outlets%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Express%2C%20Times%20Now%2C%20Republic%20and%20DNA%2C%20among%20others%20dubbed%20the%20doctored%20Amit%20Shah%20video%2C%20a%20deepfake.%20While%20speaking%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Satara%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20also%20referred%20to%20this%20video%20as%20being%20altered%20using%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20upon%20analysing%20the%20video%2C%20BOOM%20found%20that%20it%20has%20been%20doctored%20by%20splicing%20different%20portions%20of%20his%20speech%2C%20in%20order%20to%20decontextualise%20a%20statement%20made%20by%20Shah%20on%20ending%20reservations%20for%20Muslims%20in%20Telangana%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%202023%20legislative%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%20Our%20analysis%20confirms%20that%20the%20video%20was%20not%20a%20'deepfake'%20-%20as%20in%2C%20it%20was%20not%20altered%20or%20created%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20or%20deep%20learning%20algorithms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20media%20at%20a%20Diwali%20Milan%20organised%20by%20BJP%20at%20its%20national%20headquarters%20in%20New%20Delhi%20November%2C%20Modi%20highlighted%20the%20threats%20of%20'deepfakes'.%20As%20an%20example%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20cite%20a%20video%20he%20had%20seen%2C%20purportedly%20of%20himself%20dancing%20garba%2C%20and%20called%20it%20a%20deepfake.%20BOOM%20had%20fact-checked%20this%20video%2C%20and%20found%20out%20that%20it%20was%20neither%20a%20deepfake%2C%20nor%20edited%2C%20but%20showed%20a%20real%20video%20of%20a%20Narendra%20Modi-lookalike%20named%20Vikas%20Mahante%20dancing%20garba%20at%20a%20Diwali%20event%20in%20the%20UK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20before%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20elections%2C%20a%20video%20of%20Dinesh%20Lal%20Yadav%2C%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Azamgarh%2C%20went%20viral%2C%20where%20he%20could%20be%20seen%20speaking%20on%20how%20Modi%20and%20UP%20CM%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20have%20preferred%20to%20be%20childless%20to%20stop%20unemployment.%20After%20this%20video%20was%20widely%20shared%20by%20Congress%20supporters%2C%20BJP%20IT%20Cell%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20tweeted%20out%20claiming%20the%20video%20was%20a%20deepfake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBOOM%20analysed%20the%20video%20using%20deepfake%20detection%20tools%2C%20and%20also%20retrieved%20the%20original%20video%20file%20from%20the%20reporter%20who%20shot%20it%2C%20which%20confirmed%20that%20the%20video%20was%20authentic.%20Although%20the%20sequence%20of%20his%20comments%20were%20rearranged%20in%20the%20viral%20video%2C%20it%20was%20not%20a%20deepfake%2C%20nor%20did%20it%20change%20the%20meaning%20of%20his%20remarks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20absolutely%20expect%20the%20term%20'deepfakes'%20to%20be%20misused.%20Just%20as%20terms%20like%20'misinformation'%20or%20'fake%20news'%20were%20used%20to%20dismiss%20any%20evidence%20that%20a%20political%20actor%20didn't%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Prateek%20Waghre%2C%20Executive%20Director%2C%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20BOOM%2C%20Waghre%20highlights%20two%20different%20types%20of%20cases%20of%20misusing%20the%20term%20'deepfakes'.%20%26quot%3BOne%20could%20be%20the%20lack%20of%20awareness%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20nuance%20of%20the%20difference%20between%20an%20edited%20version%2C%20a%20'cheapfake'%20and%20a%20deepfake.%20The%20other%20is%20the%20outright%20dismissing%20of%20evidence%20by%20calling%20it%20a%20deepfake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Real%20Political%20Deepfakes%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20deepfakes%20in%20politics%20is%20not%20new.%20The%20first%20use%20of%20such%20technology%20in%20the%20context%20of%20an%20election%20was%20seen%20on%20February%207%2C%202020%20-%20a%20day%20before%20Delhi%20headed%20for%20legislative%20polls.%20Several%20videos%20appeared%20showing%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Manoj%20Tiwari%20criticising%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20and%20its%20leader%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20and%20urging%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP.%20These%20videos%20showed%20Tiwari%20speak%20in%20English%2C%20Hindi%20and%20a%20Hindi%20dialect%20from%20Haryana.%20However%2C%20Vice%20found%20that%20only%20the%20Hindi%20version%20was%20originally%20shot%20by%20Tiwari%20-%20the%20English%20and%20Hariyanvi%20versions%20were%20actually%20fabricated%20using%20a%20'lip-sync'%20deepfake%20algorithm%20trained%20on%20videos%20of%20Tiwari's%20speeches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20nor%20the%20BJP%20has%20officially%20commented%20on%20Tiwari's%20deepfake%20videos.%20More%20recently%2C%20BOOM%20has%20fact-checked%20multiple%20videos%20that%20were%20made%20or%20altered%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20shared%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20ongoing%20polls.%20Less%20than%20a%20week%20before%20the%20polls%20kicked-off%2C%20a%20video%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20appeared%20on%20social%20media%2C%20where%20he%20can%20be%20heard%20announcing%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20party.%20BOOM%20found%20that%20the%20video%20actually%20showed%20Gandhi%20filing%20his%20election%20nomination%20from%20Wayanad%2C%20Kerala%2C%20which%20was%20overlaid%20with%20AI%20voice%20cloning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20days%20before%20the%20election%2C%20two%20videos%20went%20viral%20showing%20Bollywood%20actors%20Aamir%20Khan%20and%20Ranveer%20Singh%20criticising%20the%20BJP-led%20government.%20BOOM%20analysed%20both%20these%20videos%2C%20and%20found%20evidence%20of%20them%20being%20altered%20using%20AI%20voice%20cloning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20hit%20social%20media%20between%20the%20first%20and%20second%20phase%20of%20elections%2C%20where%20Congress%20leader%20Kamal%20Nath%20can%20be%20heard%20promising%20land%20to%20Muslims%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20mosque%2C%20and%20the%20reinstatement%20of%20Article%20370.%20BOOM%20found%20that%20this%20video%20was%20also%20altered%2C%20with%20Nath's%20voice%20being%20replaced%20by%20an%20AI%20voice%20cloned%20replica.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20yet%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20acknowledging%20the%20emergence%20of%20such%20AI-led%20disinformation%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20polls.%20Even%20before%20elections%20in%20India%20deepfakes%20were%20peddled%20during%20polls%20in%20neighbouring%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20earlier%20this%20year.%20How%20Can%20We%20Regulate%20Deepfakes%3F%20Regulation%20of%20AI%20has%20been%20a%20hot%20topic%20of%20debate%20in%20India%2C%20following%20a%20botched%20advisory%20attempt%20by%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekhar%2C%20which%20led%20to%20massive%20confusion%20and%20multiple%20clarifications%20from%20the%20minister.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20you%20choose%20to%20use%20the%20term%20'deepfake'%2C%20whether%20you%20look%20at%20the%20broader%20issue%20of%20'synthetic%20media'%2C%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20clarity%20around%20the%20concepts%20we're%20trying%20to%20regulate.%20And%20today%20that's%20getting%20muddied%20by%20the%20public%20discourse%20around%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Waghre%20points%20out.%20The%20novelty%20of%20AI%20tools%20has%20left%20many%20perplexed%20at%20what%20exactly%20is%20being%20discussed%2C%20and%20the%20deliberate%20misuse%20of%20the%20term%20'deepfake'%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20it%20worse.%20How%20then%20can%20be%20rein%20in%20on%20the%20abuse%20of%20such%20technology%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20now-revoked%20advisory%20by%20MeitY%2C%20Radhika%20Jhalani%2C%20Volunteer%20Legal%20Counsel%2C%20SFLC.in%2C%20highlights%20the%20evolving%20nature%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bthe%20potential%20to%20change%20every%20day%2C%20and%20recommends%20a%20balanced%20approach%20to%20new%20laws.%20%26quot%3BEspecially%20with%202024%20being%20a%20major%20election%20year%20globally%2C%20deepfakes%20are%20a%20cause%20of%20concern.%20Any%20legislation%20that%20is%20implemented%20needs%20to%20balance%20misuse%20of%20tech%20with%20free%20speech%2C%26quot%3B%20Radhika%20tells%20BOOM.%20Waghre%20believes%20we%20should%20avoid%20rushing%20into%20new%20regulations%2C%20and%20rather%20examine%20existing%20laws%20to%20find%20the%20regulatory%20gaps.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20the%20different%20ways%20it%20(deepfake)%20is%20being%20used%20in%20a%20harmful%20context.%20And%20what%20does%20the%20existing%20laws%20say%20about%20forgery%2C%20and%20identity%20theft%20etc%3F%20Then%20you%20recognise%20the%20regulatory%20gaps%2C%20where%20the%20laws%20are%20currently%20falling%20short.%20Do%20we%20need%20new%20laws%20for%20cover%20them%2C%20do%20we%20need%20to%20amend%20the%20laws%2C%20or%20improve%20the%20redressal%20mechanism%2C%26quot%3B%20Waghre%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(This%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boomlive.in%2Fnews%2Fdeepfakes-or-real-edited-videos-amit-shah-bjp-congress-rahul-gandhi-lok-sabha-elections-2024-ai-25107%5C%22%3EBOOM%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20republished%20by%20NDTV%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Shakti%20Collective.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714891320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fqho87m1g_amit-shah-fact-check_625x300_27_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-problem-with-wrongly-labelling-real-or-edited-videos-as-deepfakes-5592455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20edited%20video%20of%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20went%20viral%20recently%2C%20falsely%20showing%20him%20promising%20an%20end%20to%20reservations%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-problem-with-wrongly-labelling-real-or-edited-videos-as-deepfakes-5592455%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-problem-with-wrongly-labelling-real-or-edited-videos-as-deepfakes-5592455%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-problem-with-wrongly-labelling-real-or-edited-videos-as-deepfakes-5592455%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unprecedented%20job%20creation%20recorded%20under%20Modi%20govt%3A%20Surjit%20Bhalla%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714891245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F11%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1712855238-1434.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Funprecedented-job-creation-recorded-under-modi-govt-surjit-bhalla-124050500140_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhalla%20further%20said%20the%20least%20number%20of%20jobs%20were%20created%20during%202004-2013%20(UPA%20government%20period)%2C%20and%20it%20was%20then%20that%20the%20term%20'jobless%20growth'%20came%20about%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b