allegedly%20in%20the%20video%2C%20swiftly%20responded%20by%20filing%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20claiming%20manipulation%20through%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20purportedly%20shows%20the%20BJP%20leader%20admitting%20that%20no%20rapes%20or%20sexual%20harassment%20had%20taken%20place%20and%20women%20were%20convinced%20to%20file%20such%20complaints%20at%20the%20directions%20of%20senior%20party%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kayl%2C%20in%20his%20complaint%2C%20claimed%20that%20his%20facial%20features%20and%20voice%20were%20manipulated%20using%20AI%20technology%20to%20fabricate%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20across%20a%20video...%20where%20it%20can%20be%20seen%20that%20the%20same%20has%20been%20made%20using%20my%20face%20and%20the%20voice%20has%20been%20modulated%20using%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20the%20intention%20was%20to%20mislead%20the%20public%20and%20disrupt%20ongoing%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kayl%20also%20accused%20Trinamool's%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20of%20orchestrating%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20protect%20the%20actual%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20incident.%20He%20highlighted%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20video%2C%20citing%20desynchronization%20between%20audio%20and%20video%2C%20obscured%20facial%20features%2C%20and%20poor%20audio%20quality%2C%20alluding%20to%20deliberate%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20face%20of%20the%20speaker%2C%20cannot%20be%20seen%20properly%20and%20has%20been%20edited%20in%20such%20a%20way%20so%20that%20the%20face%20remains%20in%20the%20dark.%20Audio%20quality%20is%20not%20clear%20and%20to%20suffice%20that%20subtitles%20have%20been%20used%20and%20the%20same%20has%20been%20couched%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20can%20disturb%20the%20ongoing%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20Sandeshkhali%20leader%20further%2C%20urged%20the%20CBI%20to%20investigate%20the%20said%20video%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20surfaced%20at%20a%20time%20when%20West%20Bengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20who%20had%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20state%20government%20over%20the%20Sandeskhali%20allegations%2C%20was%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20a%20temporary%20employee%20of%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20had%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20raped%20and%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20TMC%20strongman%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20aides.%20This%20prompted%20massive%20protests%20by%20the%20Bengal%20BJP%20and%20snowballed%20into%20a%20major%20national%20political%20issue%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20also%20attacked%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20Ms%20Banerjee%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20shielding%20the%20leader%2C%20who%20was%20eventually%20arrested%20in%20February%20after%20being%20on%20the%20run%20for%20over%2050%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714890060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fl8k5fbp8_sandeshkhali_625x300_21_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fslugfest-over-sandeshkhali-sting-bjp-leader-seeks-probe-into-ai-video-5592228%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20twist%20in%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20incident%20has%20thrown%20the%20political%20arena%20into%20turmoil%20as%20a%20'sting%20video'%20has%20emerged%2C%20sparking%20heated%20debates%20and%20accusations%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fslugfest-over-sandeshkhali-sting-bjp-leader-seeks-probe-into-ai-video-5592228%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww