0to%20Puducherry.%20It%20would%20be%20lovely%20to%20have%20a%20place%20of%20my%20own%2C%20she%20thought.%20But%20months%20of%20scouting%20for%20apartments%20yielded%20no%20results.%20Until%20one%20day%2C%20in%202004%2C%20when%20Jyoti%20spotted%20a%20crumbling%20home%20that%20was%20up%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owner%2C%20an%20elderly%20woman%20in%20her%20seventies%20was%20looking%20to%20relocate%20to%20Marseille%20in%20France%20where%20her%20children%20had%20moved.%20Elated%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpure%20coincidence%E2%80%9D%2C%20Jyoti%20made%20an%20offer%20for%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20spur-of-the-moment%20decision%2C%20she%20says%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344261%2Fbest-resorts-in-andaman-islands-barefoot-havelock-by-samit-sawhny-sustainable-slow-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20special%20vibe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20made%20it%20impossible%20to%20walk%20away%20even%20though%20I%20had%20set%20out%20looking%20for%20a%20smaller%20and%20easier-to-maintain%20apartment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20blame%20her.%20The%20200-year-old%20tale%20of%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20would%20pale%20any%20history%20lesson%20in%20comparison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20watched%20the%20world%20evolve%3B%20from%20the%2018th%20century%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Puducherry%20was%20rife%20with%20traders%2C%20engineers%20and%20builders%20who%20came%20to%20work%20with%20the%20French%20East%20India%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20present%20day.%20It%20is%20undeniable%20that%20the%20French%20left%20their%20indelible%20imprint%20on%20the%20city%3B%20the%20town%20still%20reflects%20French%20sensibilities%20in%20the%20language%2C%20art%2C%20culture%20and%20the%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permal